WEBVTT

00:10.792 --> 00:14.041
CAPTIONING MADE POSSIBLE BY
LIONS GATE ENTERTAINMENT

00:26.000 --> 00:30.875
[TRAIN WHISTLE]

00:30.875 --> 00:34.041
[TRAIN RUSHING BY]

00:34.041 --> 00:36.500
[RADIO FLIPPING CHANNELS]

01:31.959 --> 01:34.625
HEY, DADDY!
LOOK AT ME!

03:10.250 --> 03:13.917
Woman: I'M NOT WEARING
ANY UNDERWEAR.

03:13.917 --> 03:15.291
ARE YOU GONNA BE ABLE
TO CONCENTRATE?

03:17.125 --> 03:17.875
NOT IF YOU AREN'T HERE.

03:17.875 --> 03:21.709
[CHUCKLES]
I'M ON MY WAY.

03:21.709 --> 03:23.083
WE HIT SOME WEATHER
IN WASHINGTON,

03:23.083 --> 03:25.333
SO I JUST
GOT OFF THE PLANE.

03:25.333 --> 03:27.166
I DON'T THINK
I'LL MAKE CURTAIN,

03:27.166 --> 03:29.041
BUT I WON'T
MISS YOUR ENTRANCE.

03:29.041 --> 03:32.000
HAVE I EVER MISSED?
HA HA HA HA!

03:36.333 --> 03:38.750
WHAT'S WRONG?

03:38.750 --> 03:39.792
IT IS THE LAST SHOW.

03:39.792 --> 03:43.083
AH, ARE YOU SAD FOR US
OR FOR THE SHOW?

03:43.083 --> 03:45.250
FOR US.

03:45.250 --> 03:47.542
OH, I'M TOUCHED.

03:47.542 --> 03:48.750
[BEEP ON PHONE]

03:48.750 --> 03:50.542
HOLD ON.

03:51.917 --> 03:54.333
HANG ON, VICTOR.

03:56.625 --> 03:57.709
HEY, WHAT'S UP?

03:57.709 --> 03:59.291
THE CLIENT DOESN'T LIKE
LONDON RIGHT NOW.

03:59.291 --> 04:00.542
IS PARIS SET UP?

04:00.542 --> 04:02.000
YEAH. I JUST HAVE TO
TALK TO BRIAN.

04:02.000 --> 04:04.000
ALREADY DID.
ALREADY DID.

04:04.000 --> 04:05.041
HE'S FINE WITH IT.

04:05.041 --> 04:06.875
VERY MUCH LOOKING FORWARD
TO SEEING US IN NEW YORK

04:06.875 --> 04:08.208
FOR A LITTLE
CHAMPAGNE TOAST.

04:08.208 --> 04:09.625
I SAID FRIDAY
WOULD BE OK.

04:09.625 --> 04:10.208
SOUNDS FINE.

04:10.208 --> 04:12.625
I'LL CALL YOU LATER, OK?

04:12.625 --> 04:12.959
[BEEP]

04:12.959 --> 04:14.959
RUSSELL?

04:14.959 --> 04:16.709
I'M SORRY, BABY.

04:16.709 --> 04:17.375
THAT YOUR HUSBAND?

04:17.375 --> 04:20.041
UH-HUH. NOW,
WHERE WERE WE?

04:20.041 --> 04:23.166
OH, YEAH, MY UNDERWEAR.

04:30.083 --> 04:32.500
LOOK, I DIDN'T
WANT TO TELL YOU THIS
OVER THE PHONE, BUT...

04:35.542 --> 04:39.583
I'VE FALLEN IN LOVE
WITH YOU.

04:39.583 --> 04:40.709
[BEEPING]

04:40.709 --> 04:42.625
SHIT. HOLD ON.

04:42.625 --> 04:43.166
[BEEP]

04:43.166 --> 04:44.291
WHAT IS IT, VICTOR?

04:44.291 --> 04:47.750
I AM COUNTING ON YOU
FOR DINNER, YOU KNOW.

04:47.750 --> 04:49.667
WHY?

04:49.667 --> 04:51.417
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, WHY?

04:51.417 --> 04:52.959
GEORGE IS DAWDLING
ON THIS THING.

04:52.959 --> 04:56.208
HE DESIRES YOU, AND I THINK
HE CAN CLOSE IT TONIGHT.
THAT'S WHY.

04:56.208 --> 04:58.625
UM, YOU KNOW,
I DON'T THINK
I CAN MAKE IT,

04:58.625 --> 05:00.667
BUT, UH, I'LL TRY TO
MAKE DESSERT, OK?

05:00.667 --> 05:02.333
DON'T WAIT FOR ME.

05:06.000 --> 05:08.125
GEORGE? THANKS FOR HOLDING.

05:08.125 --> 05:11.458
LISTEN, 9:00 MIGHT BE BETTER
IF IT'S NOT TOO LATE.

05:11.458 --> 05:11.792
GOOD.

05:11.792 --> 05:14.041
[BEEP]

05:14.041 --> 05:15.667
RUSSELL?

05:15.667 --> 05:17.792
YE-E-ES?

05:17.792 --> 05:18.834
WE HAD A DEAL, REMEMBER?

05:18.834 --> 05:22.583
SO YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO DEAL WITH ME PINING

05:22.583 --> 05:24.750
AND MOONING OVER WHAT WE
MIGHT HAVE HAD TOGETHER.

05:29.417 --> 05:31.333
YOU DIDN'T HANG UP.

05:32.750 --> 05:35.792
NOT YET.

05:37.834 --> 05:39.583
SO WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

05:39.583 --> 05:41.709
I CAN'T DO THIS.

05:43.375 --> 05:46.458
WELL, IF YOU'RE
GONNA BAIL...

05:46.458 --> 05:48.500
YOU'D BEST DO IT NOW.

05:48.500 --> 05:50.166
[BEEP]

05:52.333 --> 05:53.625
SWEET.

05:53.625 --> 05:54.625
[HANGS UP]

05:54.625 --> 05:58.000
BUT YOU DIDN'T
SCARE HER AWAY.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.834
IT SOUNDED TOO MUCH
LIKE YOU MEANT IT.

05:59.834 --> 06:01.250
I DID.

06:04.500 --> 06:06.000
WELL...

06:06.000 --> 06:07.959
THEN I FEEL LIKE CUPID.

06:09.125 --> 06:10.125
PLEASE.

06:10.125 --> 06:12.875
DON'T HURT HER,
IF THAT'S WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

06:16.000 --> 06:18.667
DO YOU BELIEVE IN GOD?

06:18.667 --> 06:19.542
YES, I DO.

06:21.542 --> 06:23.875
LIFE IS
A WALKING SHADOW...

06:23.875 --> 06:28.709
A POOR PLAYER
THAT STRUTS AND FRETS
HIS HOUR UPON THE STAGE,

06:28.709 --> 06:30.583
THEN IS HEARD NO MORE.

06:30.583 --> 06:33.834
IT'S A TALE
TOLD BY AN IDIOT

06:33.834 --> 06:36.041
FULL OF SOUND AND FURY.

06:36.041 --> 06:39.250
SIGNIFYING...

06:39.250 --> 06:39.709
NOTHING.

06:45.000 --> 06:47.917
IF YOU MOVE OR SPEAK,
THIS BLOWS.

06:50.917 --> 06:53.542
IT'S VERY SENSITIVE.

06:53.542 --> 06:59.250
FOR THE NEXT FEW MOMENTS,
YOU'RE GONNA BE CLOSER
TO YOUR GOD

06:59.250 --> 07:01.500
THAN YOU'VE EVER BEEN.

07:04.917 --> 07:05.583
DON'T WASTE IT.

07:22.583 --> 07:25.583
Man: EARLY CURTAIN
TONIGHT, EVERYONE.

07:25.583 --> 07:27.500
LET'S GET GOIN'.

07:28.917 --> 07:30.917
[FAINTLY] Help.

07:35.041 --> 07:38.083
[WHISTLING]

07:57.250 --> 07:58.917
WHAT, MOTHERFUCKER?

08:00.333 --> 08:02.250
SHIT. SAY SOMETHIN', FOOL.

08:10.208 --> 08:13.208
Man: HEY, DWAYNE, HOW'S
THE SALMONELLA BUSINESS?

08:13.208 --> 08:15.375
HEY, PAPACHULO.

08:15.375 --> 08:16.500
I GOT KOSHER, MAN.

08:16.500 --> 08:19.792
I GOT TURKEY,
100% BEEF, YOU KNOW,

08:19.792 --> 08:21.792
AND ALL THAT GOOD STUFF.

08:21.792 --> 08:22.917
WHAT? NO VEGETARIAN?

08:22.917 --> 08:23.959
I GOT VEGAN, BABY.

08:23.959 --> 08:24.750
BEST ON THE MARKET.

08:24.750 --> 08:26.834
YOU CAN'T
TELL THE DIFFERENCE.

08:26.834 --> 08:27.834
FORGET IT.

08:27.834 --> 08:29.041
ME? I'M GONNA GO
ALL THE WAY--

08:29.041 --> 08:31.333
100% BEEF.

08:31.333 --> 08:32.582
LIPS.

08:32.582 --> 08:34.125
IT'S TRUE.

08:34.125 --> 08:36.582
WHAT DO YOU THINK THEY
DO WITH THE LIPS, MAN...

08:36.582 --> 08:38.457
ANUS AND SPLEEN
AND ALL THAT STUFF?

08:38.457 --> 08:41.082
IT'S ALL 100% COW.

08:42.417 --> 08:43.500
VERY FUNNY.

08:43.500 --> 08:45.750
I'LL SEE YOU
NEXT WEEK.

08:45.750 --> 08:47.875
MY REGARDS
TO YOUR BOSS.

08:56.500 --> 08:58.834
Man: RUSSELL...

08:58.834 --> 09:01.375
HAS ANYONE SEEN RUSSELL?

09:01.375 --> 09:04.041
Woman: DID YOU LOSE
MY LITTLE DARLING
AGAIN?

09:04.041 --> 09:06.208
HE TOLD ME HE'D BE BACK
BY NOW. HAVE YOU SEEN HIM?

09:06.208 --> 09:08.125
IN THE CARNAL SENSE?

09:08.125 --> 09:09.917
NO.

09:09.917 --> 09:10.750
NOT YET.

09:10.750 --> 09:13.875
HEY! FIND THE ICE QUEEN
RICH BITCH,

09:13.875 --> 09:16.333
AND YOU'LL FIND HIM.

09:17.083 --> 09:18.250
RUSSELL?

09:18.250 --> 09:19.250
[FAINTLY] Help.

09:19.250 --> 09:20.500
[TRIES HANDLE]

09:20.500 --> 09:23.959
RUSSELL, PLEASE DON'T
DO THIS TO ME AGAIN.

09:23.959 --> 09:28.458
RUSSELL, YOU WILL
PERSONALLY BE RESPONSIBLE
FOR MY HEART ATTACK.

09:28.458 --> 09:31.583
5 MINUTES, EVERYONE!

10:15.750 --> 10:17.792
SHE'S STILL NOT
IN HER SEAT?

10:22.083 --> 10:24.333
HE LEFT A MESSAGE ON MY CELL
10 MINUTES AGO

10:24.333 --> 10:26.667
SAYING HE WOULD BE HERE
10 MINUTES AGO.

10:26.667 --> 10:27.583
SHIT!

10:27.583 --> 10:30.208
OK, 5 MORE MINUTES,
EVERYONE!

10:30.208 --> 10:32.041
SHOULD I
BE GETTING DRESSED?

10:32.041 --> 10:32.959
FUCK OFF.

10:32.959 --> 10:36.834
OK. I'LL GET DRESSED
ANYWAY, JUST IN CASE.

11:21.208 --> 11:21.709
SURE YOU WON'T SPOT ME
ANOTHER GRAM?

11:21.709 --> 11:22.291
IT'S THE WEEKEND.

11:22.291 --> 11:24.959
CAN'T DO THAT, MAN.

11:24.959 --> 11:26.667
I GOT A BIG DATE, BRO.

11:26.667 --> 11:28.917
LOOK, I'M GONNA
TELL YOU SOMETHIN',
MAN.

11:28.917 --> 11:32.333
MY BOSS IS A MEAN
SON OF A BITCH,
ALL RIGHT?

11:32.333 --> 11:33.500
I GOT KIDS,
YOU KNOW?

11:33.500 --> 11:35.959
100. I'LL GIVE YOU
THE REST MONDAY.

11:35.959 --> 11:37.041
UH...NO. END OF DAY.

11:37.041 --> 11:39.041
DON'T BE WAVIN'
THAT SHIT AROUND HERE,
MAN.

11:39.041 --> 11:40.583
JESUS.

11:40.583 --> 11:43.083
HEY, I SWEAR...

11:43.083 --> 11:44.959
YOU THE MAN, DWAYNE.
WHATEVER.

12:13.208 --> 12:14.208
HELLO, DWAYNE.

12:14.208 --> 12:15.542
HEY.

12:15.542 --> 12:19.625
AH, IT'S BEEN A WEEK
ALREADY?

12:19.625 --> 12:20.709
YEAH. [CHUCKLES]

12:20.709 --> 12:22.125
THE LAST PERFORMANCE
TONIGHT.

12:22.125 --> 12:23.750
WE'RE HAVING
A BIG PARTY.

12:23.750 --> 12:24.709
YEAH?

12:24.709 --> 12:27.500
WELL, THEY GOT
SOME BIG NUMBERS

12:27.500 --> 12:28.875
COMIN' IN FROM
NEW YORK, NEXT.

12:28.875 --> 12:29.875
OH, YEAH?

12:29.875 --> 12:31.625
YEAH.

12:31.625 --> 12:33.083
BIG DEAL.

12:34.250 --> 12:36.834
[SNORTING]

12:36.834 --> 12:38.083
AHH...OH!

12:39.417 --> 12:39.917
WOW.

12:43.750 --> 12:46.083
YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF, HUH?

12:49.417 --> 12:50.709
HEH.

12:50.709 --> 12:53.709
WE GOT A GOOD THING
GOIN' ON, YOU AND ME,
HUH?

12:57.792 --> 12:59.792
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

12:59.792 --> 13:00.959
LIBERTY WALLACE.

13:00.959 --> 13:02.750
NICE TO MEET YOU,
LIBERTY WALLACE.

13:02.750 --> 13:04.291
MY NAME IS JOE.

13:04.291 --> 13:05.583
WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU, JOE?

13:05.583 --> 13:07.375
STAND STILL.

13:07.375 --> 13:09.542
EXCUSE ME?

13:12.875 --> 13:14.834
I'LL NEED YOU
TO PAY ATTENTION.

13:14.834 --> 13:18.083
LOOK, I'M LATE FOR A PLAY.
WHO IS THIS?

13:18.083 --> 13:20.417
YOU MEAN YOU'RE LATE
FOR YOUR WEEKLY FUCK?

13:20.417 --> 13:22.667
ASSHOLE.

13:29.166 --> 13:30.375
[BEEP]

13:30.375 --> 13:33.333
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

13:34.417 --> 13:37.125
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

13:37.125 --> 13:39.291
LOOK, ASSHOLE,
WHOEVER YOU ARE,

13:39.291 --> 13:40.500
IF YOU CALL HERE
ONE MORE TIME--

13:40.500 --> 13:42.625
I DIDN'T EXPECT
TO LIKE RUSSELL,

13:42.625 --> 13:45.000
BUT, THEN AGAIN, I
GUESS YOU DIDN'T EXPECT
TO LIKE HIM, EITHER.

13:48.417 --> 13:49.583
Joe: OH...DWAYNE...

13:49.583 --> 13:52.458
HAD TO TAKE A WHIZ,
SO...

13:52.458 --> 13:54.125
[GASPS]

13:54.125 --> 13:57.291
HE NEEDS YOU
TO STEP IN.

14:03.917 --> 14:06.000
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

14:06.000 --> 14:07.291
UM...

14:10.125 --> 14:13.125
WALK OVER TO
THE HOT DOG STAND.

14:15.125 --> 14:17.208
YOU NEED TO BE CLOSER.

14:27.083 --> 14:29.166
AAH!

14:29.166 --> 14:30.834
YOU NEED TO KNOW
I'VE LOCKED A SIGNAL

14:30.834 --> 14:33.166
ONTO YOUR CELL NUMBER.

14:33.166 --> 14:34.917
THERE'S A BOMB,

14:34.917 --> 14:37.709
A REALLY BIG BOMB...

14:37.709 --> 14:41.250
IN THAT HOT DOG STAND.

14:41.250 --> 14:43.875
I'LL SHOOT
INNOCENT PEOPLE.

14:43.875 --> 14:47.750
WE'VE GOT A BIT
OF GROUND TO COVER,

14:47.750 --> 14:50.917
SO I DON'T WANT TO
HAVE TO KILL YOU.

14:50.917 --> 14:51.417
WALK...

14:51.417 --> 14:52.375
CLOSER

14:52.375 --> 14:55.041
TO THE STAND.

14:56.709 --> 14:58.750
IF YOUR CELL PHONE
GOES DEAD,

14:58.750 --> 15:00.375
OR YOU TOUCH
THE MUTE BUTTON
FOR ANY REASON,

15:00.375 --> 15:02.583
IT'LL BLOW.

15:02.583 --> 15:03.834
IT'S IRREVERSIBLE.

15:03.834 --> 15:07.917
TRANSLATION:
NO "OFF" SWITCH.

15:07.917 --> 15:11.875
THERE'S ENOUGH EXPLOSIVE
IN THERE TO TAKE OUT
THE WHOLE BLOCK.

15:11.875 --> 15:14.208
SO...

15:14.208 --> 15:18.750
YOU HAVE
A LITTLE PROBLEM
ON YOUR HANDS.

15:18.750 --> 15:20.417
NOW...

15:20.417 --> 15:22.417
TAKE A BREATH.

15:22.417 --> 15:25.250
LIBERTY,
COULD YOU PLEASE
CHECK YOUR BATTERY?

15:25.250 --> 15:28.500
'CAUSE WE NEED TO KNOW
HOW MUCH TIME WE HAVE.

15:28.500 --> 15:30.250
IT'S HALF-CHARGED.

15:32.417 --> 15:34.625
WELL, THAT GIVES US
ABOUT 80 MINUTES.

15:34.625 --> 15:37.041
THERE'S A PAIR OF CUFFS
HANGING ON THE CART.

15:43.000 --> 15:46.166
YOU HAVE QUITE
A DECISION TO MAKE.

15:46.166 --> 15:49.000
TELL ME WHAT YOU WANT.

15:49.000 --> 15:51.291
YOUR SOUL.

15:51.291 --> 15:52.750
FINE. NAME A PRICE.

15:52.750 --> 15:56.583
DO YOU REALLY THINK
I'D GO THROUGH ALL THIS
TROUBLE FOR CASH?

15:56.583 --> 15:58.834
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO
PUT ON THAT ANKLE CUFF,

15:58.834 --> 16:03.041
AND THEN WE'RE
GONNA HAVE A TALK.

16:03.041 --> 16:04.125
DO IT.

16:04.125 --> 16:05.959
DO IT.

16:05.959 --> 16:07.333
NO!

16:07.333 --> 16:08.458
OK, OK.

16:21.291 --> 16:22.750
NO.

16:22.750 --> 16:25.792
ON YOUR ANKLE,
PLEASE.

16:35.542 --> 16:36.709
Joe: TUG.

16:36.709 --> 16:39.250
SHOW ME IT'S SECURE.

16:41.625 --> 16:43.208
GOOD.

16:44.667 --> 16:48.834
OK, NOW I'LL MAKE
AN HONEST MAN OF MYSELF.

16:48.834 --> 16:51.250
OPEN THE TOP LEFT DOOR
OF THE CART.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.875
Liberty: JESUS.

16:55.875 --> 16:58.250
I'M GUESSING YOU
KNOW WHAT THAT IS.

16:58.250 --> 17:03.667
I TAKE IT YOU HAVE
SOME POLITICAL AFFILIATIONS.

17:03.667 --> 17:04.666
NO.

17:04.666 --> 17:08.416
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

17:08.834 --> 17:11.750
I NEED YOURS.

17:17.083 --> 17:18.916
LOOK, IF WE COULD JUST
CUT TO THE CHASE HERE?

17:18.916 --> 17:20.625
I'M GUESSING
YOU HAVE A 223.

17:20.625 --> 17:23.250
SOPHISTICATED.

17:23.250 --> 17:24.625
YOU MEAN EXPENSIVE.

17:24.625 --> 17:26.375
THAT, TOO, WHICH MEANS
YOU'RE CONNECTED.

17:26.375 --> 17:27.709
OH, YEAH.
ALL RIGHT,

17:27.709 --> 17:29.542
YOU'VE GOT ME STANDING STILL.
WHAT'S NEXT?

17:29.542 --> 17:31.125
EASY.

17:31.125 --> 17:34.250
I GET TO DECIDE
HOW THIS GOES DOWN.

17:34.250 --> 17:35.709
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

17:35.709 --> 17:38.000
I KNOW
IT'S NOT RUSSELL,

17:38.000 --> 17:40.917
BECAUSE
HE'S BACKSTAGE THINKING
ABOUT YOUR FUTURE.

17:40.917 --> 17:43.667
HE'S WONDERIN' WHETHER
YOU PUT YOUR PANTIES
BACK ON

17:43.667 --> 17:47.250
AND AREN'T MAKING
A RUN FOR IT.

17:47.250 --> 17:49.875
I'M SURE
YOU'RE WONDERING

17:49.875 --> 17:51.500
IF I'M WORKING
FOR YOUR HUSBAND.

17:51.500 --> 17:52.709
WELL, I'M NOT.

17:52.709 --> 17:55.750
IF HE KNEW
ABOUT RUSSELL,
HE'D TAKE IT HARD.

17:55.750 --> 17:58.959
HE'S A VERY
VIOLENT MAN.

17:58.959 --> 17:59.542
HEY, IS, UH,
DWAYNE AROUND?

17:59.542 --> 18:02.000
UH...

18:02.000 --> 18:03.000
NO. HE STEPPED AWAY.

18:03.000 --> 18:06.917
WELL, IS HE GONNA
BE BACK SOON?

18:06.917 --> 18:09.083
NO.

18:11.083 --> 18:16.083
DID--DID HE LEAVE
ANYTHING FOR FRANK?

18:16.083 --> 18:17.750
SELL HIM SOMETHING.
HE'S DESPERATE.

18:17.750 --> 18:18.750
NO.

18:18.750 --> 18:19.291
WHAT?

18:28.333 --> 18:29.750
[MOUTHING WORDS]

18:31.208 --> 18:33.083
NO. UM...
I DON'T EAT MEAT.

18:33.083 --> 18:36.000
[JOE CHUCKLES]

18:36.000 --> 18:38.458
HE THINKS YOU WARNED HIM
ABOUT THE COPS.

18:42.250 --> 18:43.417
YOU HAVING FUN, JOE?

18:43.417 --> 18:46.041
YES.

18:46.041 --> 18:48.583
BUT NOT LIKE YOU THINK.

18:51.458 --> 18:53.500
HOW MUCH DO YOU WANT?

18:53.500 --> 18:56.625
NOTHING.
IT'S NOT ABOUT CASH.

18:56.625 --> 18:58.625
IT'S ABOUT YOU.

18:58.625 --> 19:00.667
YOU HAVE 2 CHOICES:

19:00.667 --> 19:03.458
FIRST, YOU DIE
AN AMERICAN HERO.

19:03.458 --> 19:05.542
SECOND...

19:05.542 --> 19:07.166
YOU DIE STILL WORKIN'
FOR THE FAT MAN.

19:07.166 --> 19:09.625
LOOK, I HAVE ACCOUNTS
ALL OVER THE WORLD.

19:09.625 --> 19:11.291
I HAVE UNLIMITED RESOURCES.
TELL ME HOW MUCH YOU WANT.

19:11.291 --> 19:13.625
IS IT ALL CHAMPAGNE
INSIDE THAT PRETTY HEAD?

19:13.625 --> 19:14.834
I DON'T SEE
WHERE THIS IS GOING.

19:14.834 --> 19:18.458
AHH...LIBERTY,

19:18.458 --> 19:18.917
MEMORY LANE.

19:18.917 --> 19:22.792
THE FORMER YOU.

19:22.792 --> 19:26.291
LIFE BEFORE
THE BULGARI HANDBAG.

19:26.291 --> 19:28.000
WHAT HAPPENED?

19:28.000 --> 19:30.208
YOU KNOW,
MY HUSBAND IS--

19:30.208 --> 19:32.041
YOU CAN'T PIN THIS
ON HIM.

19:32.041 --> 19:33.834
HE'S JUST A THUG

19:33.834 --> 19:35.500
WORKING ON ANY SIDE
OF THE LAW

19:35.500 --> 19:36.834
THAT'LL
GIVE OUT A CHECK.

19:36.834 --> 19:40.208
BY THE MEDALS HE EARNED
DURING HIS STINT
WITH THE MILITARY,

19:40.208 --> 19:42.166
SOME WOULD SAY HE'S A HERO.

19:42.166 --> 19:44.041
AND WHAT WOULD YOU SAY,
LIBERTY?

19:44.041 --> 19:47.583
I DON'T THINK THIS
IS ABOUT WHAT I THINK ABOUT
MY HUSBAND'S TRACK RECORD.

19:48.834 --> 19:50.375
DO HEROES PRAY FOR WAR

19:50.375 --> 19:52.250
SO THAT THEY
CAN SELL THEIR BULLETS?

19:52.250 --> 19:54.291
WE NEVER DISCUSS
OUR BUSINESS.

19:54.291 --> 19:54.875
OK, LIBERTY.

19:54.875 --> 19:58.375
YOU'RE IN MY SIGHT LINE,

19:58.375 --> 20:01.000
YOU'RE STANDING
NEXT TO A BOMB,

20:01.000 --> 20:02.875
AND YOU'RE
NOT AT LIBERTY

20:02.875 --> 20:05.792
TO DISCUSS THAT
YOU AND YOUR HUSBAND
MANUFACTURE GUNS

20:05.792 --> 20:08.542
AND SELL THEM
TO ANY FUCKIN' COUNTRY

20:08.542 --> 20:10.792
OR STREET ASSHOLE

20:10.792 --> 20:14.834
OR ALL-AMERICAN KID
WHO'LL PAY YOU THE CASH.

20:14.834 --> 20:15.625
PHEW...

20:15.625 --> 20:19.041
HOORAY FOR
THE AMERICAN DREAM.

20:19.041 --> 20:21.041
IF YOU WANT SOMETHING,
ASK FOR IT.

20:21.041 --> 20:22.667
OTHERWISE,
I'M JUST GONNA HANG UP.

20:22.667 --> 20:25.208
GO AHEAD.

20:37.542 --> 20:40.000
Liberty: IS THIS ABOUT
THE SALE TO POLAND?

20:40.000 --> 20:41.125
Joe: SERBIA.

20:41.125 --> 20:42.417
POLAND.

20:42.417 --> 20:45.041
[SIGHS]

20:45.041 --> 20:49.417
DENIAL
IS A CURIOUS THING.

20:49.417 --> 20:51.917
THE SHIPMENT NEVER
MADE IT TO POLAND.

20:51.917 --> 20:54.750
SERBIANS, CROATS--

20:54.750 --> 20:56.834
KIDS ON BOTH SIDES...

20:56.834 --> 20:59.083
ALL DIED.

20:59.083 --> 21:00.709
WHAT'S THE FUCKING
DIFFERENCE?

21:00.709 --> 21:01.375
SO YOU WERE THERE?

21:07.625 --> 21:09.959
[BEEPING]

21:15.458 --> 21:16.583
[BEEPING FASTER]

21:21.917 --> 21:24.417
[BEEPING SLOWLY]

21:29.208 --> 21:30.750
GO ON, HONEY.

21:32.083 --> 21:33.500
HOT DOG, PLEASE.

21:34.959 --> 21:35.959
SURE.

21:35.959 --> 21:37.709
SURE.

21:48.125 --> 21:51.000
UH, NO MUSTARD.

22:02.125 --> 22:05.750
I SAID NO MUSTARD.

22:05.750 --> 22:08.542
CUTE. DON'T MAKE ME
PULL THE TRIGGER.

22:08.542 --> 22:10.125
HE'S JUST A KID.

22:10.125 --> 22:12.166
I HAVE NOTHING
TO LOSE, LIBERTY.

22:12.166 --> 22:13.542
OR HAVEN'T YOU
FIGURED THAT OUT YET?

22:16.208 --> 22:17.709
GET OUT.

22:36.208 --> 22:37.417
YOU KNOW, YOU KNOW
A LOT ABOUT ME:

22:37.417 --> 22:40.208
WHAT I'M THINKING,
WHO I'M FUCKING.

22:40.208 --> 22:41.709
JUST AMAZING, JOE.

22:41.709 --> 22:43.709
AND I'M YOUR ONLY FRIEND
AT THIS MOMENT.

22:43.709 --> 22:45.000
MY FINAL CONFESSOR.

22:45.000 --> 22:45.959
THAT, TOO.

22:45.959 --> 22:48.542
SO, YOU WHACKING OFF
RIGHT NOW, BABY, HMM?

22:48.542 --> 22:50.208
WORKING OUT SOME
DOMINATION BULLSHIT?

22:50.208 --> 22:51.792
TREAD CAREFULLY,
DEAR HEART.

22:51.792 --> 22:53.208
WHY?
IN THIS GAME OF YOURS,

22:53.208 --> 22:54.250
THE WAY I SEE IT,
I DIE EITHER WAY.

22:54.250 --> 22:55.667
MAY AS WELL
HAVE SOME FUN.

22:55.667 --> 23:00.417
VP MARKETING.
McCLOUD--THE STANDARD
IN AMERICAN WEAPONRY,

23:00.417 --> 23:03.458
KIND OF LIKE BARETTA
IS TO THE ITALIANS.

23:03.458 --> 23:05.458
AH, SO THAT'S WHAT
THIS IS ABOUT.

23:05.458 --> 23:07.667
YOUR DILEMMA IS...

23:09.041 --> 23:10.625
WHEN TO PULL THE PLUG.
[ECHO] PULL THE PLUG...

23:10.625 --> 23:14.500
AND WHO YOU'RE GONNA
TAKE WITH YOU.

23:14.500 --> 23:15.500
AAH!

23:15.500 --> 23:16.500
UHH!

23:17.041 --> 23:20.125
WHAT WAS THAT?

23:21.125 --> 23:23.083
YEAH...

23:23.083 --> 23:26.709
YOU'VE JUST BEEN SHOT AT
BY YOUR BEST-SELLING RIFLE.

23:26.709 --> 23:28.000
HOW DOES IT FEEL?

23:28.000 --> 23:29.291
HOW'S IT SUPPOSED
TO FEEL?

23:29.291 --> 23:30.542
REAL.

23:30.542 --> 23:32.375
OK, LOOK. FINE.
I'M TERRIFIED.

23:32.375 --> 23:33.959
IS THAT WHAT
YOU WANT ME TO SAY?

23:33.959 --> 23:35.375
IT'S A START.

23:35.375 --> 23:37.333
THEN YOU GOT
A LITTLE OVER AN HOUR

23:37.333 --> 23:39.500
TO SOUND LIKE
YOU REALLY MEAN IT.

23:39.500 --> 23:43.792
YOU WANNA KNOW
WHAT MAKES ME SO TWISTED

23:43.792 --> 23:47.375
AND CRAZY?
[ECHO] CRAZY, CRAZY...

23:47.375 --> 23:49.917
THE WHY OF IT ALL.

23:49.917 --> 23:51.000
IT'S KIND OF FUNNY.

23:51.000 --> 23:52.583
RIGHT NOW, I FEEL
ABSOLUTELY SANE.

23:52.583 --> 23:55.959
BUT I KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO BE TWISTED AND CRAZY.

23:55.959 --> 23:57.625
SOMETHING
I DON'T THINK

23:57.625 --> 24:00.125
THAT YOU'VE EVER
EXPERIENCED.

24:00.125 --> 24:02.583
Liberty:
I'VE HAD MY MOMENTS.

24:02.583 --> 24:04.125
DON'T COMPETE.

24:04.125 --> 24:05.083
YOU'RE RIGHT.

24:05.083 --> 24:07.917
YOU'RE PROBABLY CRAZIER
THAN I'VE EVER BEEN.

24:07.917 --> 24:10.291
HA HA HA HA HA!

24:12.792 --> 24:15.083
I'LL TAKE THE LONG WALK,
AND THEN YOU'LL KNOW.

24:15.083 --> 24:17.750
I--I MEAN,
I DON'T HAVE TO...

24:17.750 --> 24:19.542
MY GOD, HE SUCKS.

24:19.542 --> 24:21.333
I CAN'T
GO OUT THERE.

24:22.208 --> 24:23.709
[BEEPING]

24:30.166 --> 24:32.000
Liberty: SO,
YOU'RE QUITE A SHOT.

24:32.000 --> 24:32.792
YEAH.

24:32.792 --> 24:36.792
I STARTED WITH BBs
AND SQUIRRELS.

24:36.792 --> 24:40.375
YOU'RE A PRETTY
CRACK SHOT YOURSELF.

24:41.834 --> 24:42.959
OH, YOU KNOW.

24:42.959 --> 24:44.792
MY FATHER WANTED
A COMPETITION KID,

24:44.792 --> 24:46.750
SO I WENT FOR THE MEDALS.

24:49.041 --> 24:50.792
KNOW WHAT HE DID TO ME
THE FIRST TIME

24:50.792 --> 24:53.291
HE TOOK ME OUT
IN THE BUSH?

24:53.291 --> 24:56.417
HE SHOT THIS DEER.

24:56.417 --> 24:57.750
THE DEER HAD A FAWN.

25:00.375 --> 25:03.291
YOU KNOW WHAT
HE MADE ME DO?

25:04.583 --> 25:06.208
HE MADE ME SHOOT IT...

25:06.208 --> 25:08.834
AT CLOSE RANGE.

25:08.834 --> 25:10.875
AND YOU PULLED
THE TRIGGER.

25:10.875 --> 25:12.375
I HATED HIM
FOR MAKING ME DO IT.

25:12.375 --> 25:13.458
I HAD NIGHTMARES.

25:13.458 --> 25:15.208
HOW IRONIC.

25:15.208 --> 25:16.667
[CHUCKLING] YEAH.

25:19.166 --> 25:22.208
COME ON, LET'S GET
BACK TO THE POINT.

25:22.208 --> 25:23.959
WHY ARE YOU
DOING THIS, JOE?

25:23.959 --> 25:27.375
YOU MUST MEET ALL KINDS
IN YOUR BUSINESS.

25:27.375 --> 25:28.333
WHY DO THEY?

25:28.333 --> 25:29.917
COME ON.
I SELL CORPORATELY.

25:29.917 --> 25:30.834
IT'S NOT LIKE I DEAL
WITH EVERY ASSHOLE

25:30.834 --> 25:33.667
WHO WANTS TO WAVE
A BIG DICK AT SOMETHING.

25:33.667 --> 25:35.959
SO IT'S ABOUT
MY DICK?

25:35.959 --> 25:37.667
[AUDIENCE APPLAUDS]

25:39.333 --> 25:42.000
WHAT IF RUSSEL
SLIT HIS WRISTS?

25:42.000 --> 25:43.166
WE SHOULD CALL
THE POLICE.

25:43.166 --> 25:44.709
SLIT HIS WRISTS?

25:44.709 --> 25:46.917
RUSSELL'S THE HAPPIEST MAN
I'VE EVER MET.

25:46.917 --> 25:49.917
HAPPINESS IS THE BEST COVER
FOR CLINICAL DEPRESSION.

25:49.917 --> 25:52.542
WHAT?

25:52.542 --> 25:54.208
DID HE TELL YOU
HE WAS DEPRESSED?

25:54.208 --> 25:55.542
THE MAN IS DATING
A BARRACUDA.

25:55.542 --> 25:57.083
WHAT'S NOT TO BE
DEPRESSED ABOUT?

25:57.083 --> 25:59.667
[BEEPING]

25:59.667 --> 26:00.709
[SIGHS]

26:02.875 --> 26:05.250
YOU KNOW, WE'RE IN A BIT
OF A TIME JAM HERE.

26:05.250 --> 26:07.041
THIS GUESSING GAME'S
GETTING A BIT TIRING.

26:07.041 --> 26:10.500
WHY DON'T YOU JUST TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON?

26:12.333 --> 26:14.500
FAIR ENOUGH.

26:14.500 --> 26:17.834
I WANT YOU
TO UNDERSTAND LOSS.

26:19.166 --> 26:22.041
YOU LOST SOMEONE...

26:23.750 --> 26:25.583
TO A GUN ACCIDENT?

26:25.583 --> 26:26.250
NO ACCIDENT.

26:26.250 --> 26:29.208
A WILLFUL ACT.

26:29.208 --> 26:31.458
PREMEDITATED.

26:32.834 --> 26:33.917
YOUR WIFE?

26:37.417 --> 26:38.083
SON?

26:38.083 --> 26:40.291
[SIGHS]

26:41.417 --> 26:43.375
YOUR DAUGHTER?

26:56.959 --> 26:58.750
LOOK. I'M REALLY SORRY
FOR YOU AND YOUR FAMILY,

26:58.750 --> 27:01.709
BUT IS THIS HOW
SHE'D WANT YOU TO ACT?

27:01.709 --> 27:04.250
SHE'S NOT ALIVE
TO ASK.

27:04.250 --> 27:06.333
WHY WOULD YOU WANT
MORE BLOOD ON YOUR HANDS?

27:06.333 --> 27:09.458
MISERY NEEDS COMPANY.

27:11.291 --> 27:12.542
THE BLOOD IS GOING
TO SPILL TO YOUR HANDS

27:12.542 --> 27:14.959
WHERE IT BELONGS,
LIBERTY.

27:17.083 --> 27:19.083
THERE'S HUNDREDS OF PEOPLE
WHO TRADE WEAPONS.

27:19.083 --> 27:20.750
I'M JUST ONE TINY SPECK
IN ALL OF THIS.

27:20.750 --> 27:21.542
THAT'S ALL IT TAKES.

27:21.542 --> 27:24.291
PRESIDENTS
AND 3-YEAR-OLDS DIE

27:24.291 --> 27:26.166
ALL IN THE NAME
OF THE CONSTITUTION.

27:26.166 --> 27:27.709
THEY HAVE METAL DETECTORS
AND COPS IN SCHOOLS.

27:27.709 --> 27:31.458
WHAT, IS THAT WHAT MAKES
AMERICA GREAT?

27:31.458 --> 27:32.750
OK. I GET WHERE
THIS IS GOING.

27:32.750 --> 27:36.125
I'LL DENOUNCE
MY INVOLVEMENT IN WEAPONS.

27:36.125 --> 27:37.041
I'LL, UH,
DENOUNCE THE INDUSTRY.

27:37.041 --> 27:39.959
FUCK, I'LL DENOUNCE
DEATH IN GENERAL, OK?

27:39.959 --> 27:41.250
WE'LL GET THE PRESS HERE.

27:41.250 --> 27:42.709
WE'LL CAUSE A BIG SCENE.

27:42.709 --> 27:43.959
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT?

27:43.959 --> 27:45.291
YOU'RE SO FULL OF SHIT.

27:45.291 --> 27:46.625
UH, LOOK.

27:46.625 --> 27:49.625
I KNOW YOU MUST BE
DYING INSIDE,

27:49.625 --> 27:52.125
BUT I'M STANDING NEXT
TO A GODDAMN BOMB,

27:52.125 --> 27:54.000
AND IT'S GONNA CAUSE
SOME SERIOUS DAMAGE.

27:54.000 --> 27:55.166
SO IF YOU WANT COVERAGE,

27:55.166 --> 27:57.667
COME ON,
LET'S GET IT GOING.

28:00.208 --> 28:03.375
WHAT WERE YOUR FATHER'S
LAST WORDS?

28:07.083 --> 28:09.500
HE HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

28:09.500 --> 28:11.625
YEAH. I GUESS BLOWING
YOUR BRAINS OUT IS...

28:11.625 --> 28:13.166
IS ABOUT AS MUCH AS ANY
ONE PERSON CAN EVER SAY.

28:13.166 --> 28:15.959
[CHUCKLES]

28:15.959 --> 28:20.333
YOU SEEM TO KNOW
A LOT ABOUT ME
AND MY FAMILY, JOE.

28:20.333 --> 28:21.792
IT'S PERSONAL.

28:23.083 --> 28:24.875
AND I GET TO ATONE
FOR THE SINS

28:24.875 --> 28:27.333
OF EVERY CHEAP-SUIT
FUCKING GUN SALESMAN?

28:27.333 --> 28:29.667
YEAH.
AND YOUR FATHER.

28:30.375 --> 28:31.208
HE HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

28:31.208 --> 28:33.166
FUCK YOU!

28:33.166 --> 28:35.709
THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH MY FATHER.

28:35.709 --> 28:38.125
THIS IS ABOUT YOU
GOING POSTAL!

28:39.208 --> 28:40.959
UH-UH. HE'S PART
OF THE FAMILY LEGACY.

28:40.959 --> 28:42.667
BULLSHIT.
HE IS NOT!

28:42.667 --> 28:43.500
HE IS NOT!

28:43.500 --> 28:44.875
Joe: YOU WERE AN
IMPRESSIONABLE KID.

28:44.875 --> 28:46.709
HIS MONEY BOUGHT YOU
INTO A SOCIETY

28:46.709 --> 28:48.542
ON BOTH SIDES OF THE LAW.

28:48.542 --> 28:50.750
HE'S DEFINITELY
A PART OF THIS.

28:50.750 --> 28:52.250
Liberty: NO, HE ISN'T.

29:03.875 --> 29:04.875
[MAN WHISTLES]

29:04.875 --> 29:08.041
Joe: TRY THAT $5,000 WATCH
YOU'RE WEARING.

29:09.333 --> 29:11.583
FINE.

29:11.583 --> 29:15.500
OR BETTER YET,
THAT $25,000 WEDDING RING.

29:15.500 --> 29:16.083
YOU GOT IT.

29:27.417 --> 29:30.333
[POLICE RADIO SQUAWKS]

29:34.834 --> 29:38.083
WHERE'S DWAYNE,
MS. LIBERTY WALLACE?

29:38.083 --> 29:39.417
OH, HE HAD TO STEP AWAY.

29:39.417 --> 29:41.500
I'M WATCHING THE STAND.

29:44.250 --> 29:46.959
YOU, UH, DOING THIS
FOR A REASON?

29:49.083 --> 29:51.083
Joe: YOU TELL HIM,
I SHOOT HIM.

29:55.375 --> 29:56.959
IT'S HOT.

29:56.959 --> 29:58.375
Joe: HIS LIFE
IS IN YOUR HANDS, LIBERTY..

29:58.375 --> 29:59.458
PUT YOUR CLOTHES ON.

29:59.458 --> 30:02.041
I'LL--I'LL
TAKE WHATEVER
YOU'RE SELLING.

30:02.041 --> 30:03.250
BEAT IT.

30:04.792 --> 30:06.959
A HOT DOG
FOR THE ROAD.

30:10.500 --> 30:11.959
GOOD FOR SALES?

30:11.959 --> 30:13.375
I SAID BEAT IT.

30:13.375 --> 30:14.709
ALL RIGHT.

30:14.709 --> 30:17.333
WHATEVER
YOU'RE ON, LADY,

30:17.333 --> 30:19.667
GET MORE OF IT.

30:30.458 --> 30:33.333
Joe, singsong: YOU'RE
PISSING ME OFF.

30:33.333 --> 30:35.792
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

30:35.792 --> 30:37.709
UHH.

30:37.709 --> 30:40.291
YOU'RE SIGNING
HIS DEATH WARRANT.

30:40.291 --> 30:42.208
IS THAT
WHAT YOU WANT?

30:53.417 --> 30:55.583
Joe: IT'S SHOWTIME.

31:01.333 --> 31:03.417
YOUR ACTIONS
HAVE CONSEQUENCES.

31:13.542 --> 31:15.208
UHH!

31:20.375 --> 31:22.709
YOU SHOT HIM?

31:22.709 --> 31:24.166
GOD, YOU SHOT HIM.

31:24.166 --> 31:26.041
HE'S DYING AS WE SPEAK.

31:26.041 --> 31:27.625
UHH! UNH! UNH!

31:27.625 --> 31:30.250
TELL ME WHAT YOU WANT.

31:30.250 --> 31:31.709
FOR ONE, YOUR COMPANY
JUST MADE A DEAL

31:31.709 --> 31:34.750
WORTH SEVERAL
MILLION DOLLARS.

31:34.750 --> 31:37.125
YOU'RE NOT
GOING TO DELIVER.

31:37.125 --> 31:38.083
[OFFICER GROANING]

31:40.375 --> 31:42.208
[POLICE RADIO SQUAWKING]

31:49.542 --> 31:51.458
OFFICER,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

31:51.458 --> 31:52.542
HUNH!

31:52.542 --> 31:54.667
OH, MY GOD.

31:58.583 --> 32:00.583
HELLO?

32:00.583 --> 32:01.709
YEAH.

32:01.709 --> 32:04.583
THERE'S AN OFFICER HERE.
HE'S BLEEDING.

32:04.583 --> 32:05.875
UH, I DON'T KNOW.

32:05.875 --> 32:07.667
I THINK THE CORNER
OF NINTH AND GRACE.

32:09.208 --> 32:10.750
Joe: FUCK HIM.
HE WAS A BAD COP.

32:10.750 --> 32:13.333
ADDICTED
AND ON THE TAKE.

32:13.333 --> 32:15.333
UH, MY NAME?

32:15.333 --> 32:17.625
IT'S, UM...
GEORGE.

32:19.041 --> 32:21.417
McCANISTER. LOOK.
I'M JUST STANDING HERE.

32:21.417 --> 32:23.250
I DON'T REALLY WANT--

32:23.250 --> 32:24.834
YEAH, I'LL--I'LL WAIT.

32:24.834 --> 32:27.083
I GUESS.

32:27.083 --> 32:29.083
AH, FUCK, A LOT OF PEOPLE
ARE ABOUT TO ARRIVE.

32:29.083 --> 32:32.750
THIS IS YOUR WINDOW
OF OPPORTUNITY, LIBERTY.

32:32.750 --> 32:34.166
LET'S CALL YOUR HUSBAND.

32:34.166 --> 32:35.125
NO, DON'T.

32:35.125 --> 32:36.333
I'LL 3-WAY YOU.

32:36.333 --> 32:37.458
DON'T!

32:37.458 --> 32:39.208
[SPEED-DIALING,
TELEPHONE RINGS]

32:39.208 --> 32:41.542
Secretary: McCLOUD INDUSTRIES,
VICTOR WALLACE'S OFFICE.

32:41.542 --> 32:42.208
YES. IS HE THERE,
PLEASE?

32:42.208 --> 32:45.875
WHO MAY I SAY
IS CALLING?

32:45.875 --> 32:47.875
LIBERTY.
EXCUSE ME?

32:47.875 --> 32:49.125
HIS WIFE.

32:49.125 --> 32:51.291
I'M CALLING
FOR HIS WIFE...

32:51.291 --> 32:52.709
WHO ASKED ME TO CALL

32:52.709 --> 32:56.291
BECAUSE SHE'S IN A BIT
OF A JAM RIGHT NOW.

32:56.291 --> 32:57.792
PLEASE HOLD.

32:57.792 --> 32:59.291
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

33:02.166 --> 33:07.083
Secretary: MR. WALLACE,
YOUR WIFE IS ON THE LINE, SIR.

33:07.083 --> 33:08.625
[CLEARS THROAT]

33:08.625 --> 33:09.875
[BEEP]

33:09.875 --> 33:10.875
WHAT'S UP, LIB?

33:10.875 --> 33:11.542
Joe: SHE'S ON
THE OTHER LINE,

33:11.542 --> 33:13.959
CONFERENCED.

33:13.959 --> 33:14.500
AND WHO IS THIS?

33:14.500 --> 33:16.792
I'M JOE.

33:16.792 --> 33:18.000
YOUR WIFE'S
CUFFED TO A BOMB

33:18.000 --> 33:21.709
WIRED TO BLOW
IF THE CELL PHONE DIES.

33:21.709 --> 33:24.333
I'VE ALSO GOT
ONE OF YOUR RIFLES
POINTED AT HER

33:24.333 --> 33:25.834
SO I CAN SHOOT HER...

33:25.834 --> 33:28.959
OR ANYONE ELSE I FIGURE
ISN'T WORKING OUT.

33:28.959 --> 33:30.834
LIBERTY?

33:34.000 --> 33:34.917
[BEEP]

33:34.917 --> 33:36.375
[TELEPHONE CLICKS OFF]

33:36.375 --> 33:39.208
OOPS. IS HE ALWAYS
THAT SYMPATHETIC?

33:39.208 --> 33:40.875
HE PROBABLY THINKS
YOU'RE A TERRORIST.

33:40.875 --> 33:44.583
TERRORIST?
WHY IS THAT?

33:44.583 --> 33:48.375
BECAUSE OF THE DEALS
YOU CUT WITH
SENATOR TOLLMAN?

33:48.375 --> 33:50.583
GOVERNMENT INVOLVEMENT
IS CLASSIFIED.

33:50.583 --> 33:52.667
George: HEY, THEY'RE
ON THEIR WAY, ALL RIGHT?

33:52.667 --> 33:54.000
JUST HOLD ON A SECOND.

33:54.000 --> 33:56.208
YOUR HUSBAND
JUST HUNG UP ON YOU.

33:56.208 --> 33:59.041
THAT'S BECAUSE HE THOUGHT
HE WAS PROTECTING ME.

33:59.041 --> 34:00.834
WE SIGNED
A NO-DEALS POLICY

34:00.834 --> 34:01.834
SO THAT WE WOULDN'T BE
VULNERABLE TO EVERY--

34:01.834 --> 34:05.000
EVERY FUCKING TERRORIST.

34:05.000 --> 34:06.709
IT WAS A CONDITION
FOR THE MILITARY.

34:06.709 --> 34:07.375
OH, PLEASE.

34:07.375 --> 34:09.500
WHAT DOES
SIGNING A CONTRACT

34:09.500 --> 34:11.667
REALLY HAVE TO DO
WITH IT?

34:11.667 --> 34:13.708
[CELL PHONE BEEPS]

34:13.708 --> 34:15.542
DON'T...ANSWER.

34:15.542 --> 34:17.708
[BEEP BEEP]

34:17.708 --> 34:18.958
Victor: LIBERTY.

34:18.958 --> 34:20.833
HEY, IT'S ME.
IT'S FOR REAL.

34:20.833 --> 34:22.792
I'M AT THE CORNER
OF NINTH AND GRACE.

34:22.792 --> 34:24.583
I HAVE ABOUT 45 MINUTES
LEFT ON MY BATTERY.

34:24.583 --> 34:26.542
AAAH!

34:26.542 --> 34:27.833
LIBERTY, TALK TO ME.

34:27.833 --> 34:29.542
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHO WE'RE DEALING WITH?

34:29.542 --> 34:31.083
NO.

34:37.166 --> 34:39.750
HE SAID SOMETHING ABOUT US
BAILING ON A DEAL.

34:39.750 --> 34:41.166
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S TALKING ABOUT.

34:41.166 --> 34:44.041
THE ONLY ONE BIG ENOUGH
IS THE ONE GOING THROUGH PARIS.

34:44.041 --> 34:45.375
NOTHING MORE SPECIFIC?

34:45.375 --> 34:45.875
NO!

34:45.875 --> 34:47.917
I DON'T GET IT.

34:47.917 --> 34:49.291
HOW DID YOU LEAVE IT
WITH WASHINGTON?

34:49.291 --> 34:51.041
DONE.
THE MONEY'S WIRED.

34:51.041 --> 34:53.166
WHAT DOES HE WANT?
HIJACK THE SHIPMENT?

34:53.166 --> 34:54.417
WHAT DOES HE WANT?

34:54.417 --> 34:55.792
AAAH!

34:55.792 --> 34:57.709
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE WANTS!

34:57.709 --> 35:00.792
HE WON'T TELL ME.

35:00.792 --> 35:01.333
[CRYING]
THIS COULD BE GOOD-BYE.

35:01.333 --> 35:01.917
DON'T GET DRAMATIC.

35:01.917 --> 35:03.625
IF THEY WANTED YOU DEAD,

35:03.625 --> 35:04.500
YOU WOULD BE.

35:04.500 --> 35:07.000
I'M HANGING UP NOW.
I'M ON IT. [CLICK]

35:07.000 --> 35:07.750
I DON'T FUCKING BELIEVE YOU.

35:07.750 --> 35:10.208
YOU DO THAT AGAIN...

35:10.208 --> 35:13.166
I'LL SHOOT
INNOCENT PEOPLE
ON YOUR BEHALF.

35:13.166 --> 35:17.625
Woman: YEAH. YEAH,
WE SHOULD GO BACK TOMORROW.

35:17.625 --> 35:18.500
OHH.

35:18.500 --> 35:21.000
HE DIDN'T EVEN
SAY GOOD-BYE, DID HE?

35:21.000 --> 35:24.834
WELL, HE'S GOT
A LOT AT STAKE.

35:24.834 --> 35:28.000
INTERNATIONAL ARMS DEALING
IS TRICKY BUSINESS.

35:28.000 --> 35:29.709
NO LOYALTIES.

35:37.125 --> 35:38.333
CALL BRIAN.

35:40.291 --> 35:40.750
I ALREADY DID.

35:40.750 --> 35:43.291
OH, GOOD BOY.

35:43.291 --> 35:43.625
VERY GOOD BOY.

35:43.625 --> 35:45.458
[SIGHS]

35:45.458 --> 35:47.625
THIS IS
A HOSTAGE SITUATION.

35:47.625 --> 35:49.125
YOUR HANDS ARE TIED.

35:49.125 --> 35:50.709
[SIGHS]

35:50.709 --> 35:52.625
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO DO NOW?

35:52.625 --> 35:54.834
GO AND SIP TEA
IN A SAFE HOUSE

35:54.834 --> 35:56.709
WHILE MY WIFE
IS CHAINED TO A BOMB?

35:56.709 --> 35:58.291
CALM DOWN.

35:58.291 --> 35:59.583
YOU'RE A TARGET,
TOO.

35:59.583 --> 36:01.375
SHE KNOWS THE DRILL.

36:01.375 --> 36:02.959
YOU BOTH SIGNED
THE SECURITY AGREEMENT.

36:02.959 --> 36:04.792
THE MACHINERY
JUST KICKED IN.

36:04.792 --> 36:06.792
I'M CALM.
I'M VERY CALM.

36:06.792 --> 36:08.834
[SIREN BLARES]

36:08.834 --> 36:10.250
SHIT.

36:10.250 --> 36:11.792
[POLICE RADIO SQUAWKS]

36:11.792 --> 36:14.375
Officer: STEP AWAY!

36:14.375 --> 36:16.000
DID YOU SEE
WHAT HAPPENED HERE?

36:16.000 --> 36:17.500
I DIDN'T SEE
ANYTHING.

36:17.500 --> 36:19.667
19-A-6
REQUESTS BACKUP.

36:19.667 --> 36:20.792
REQUEST
IMMEDIATE BACKUP.

36:20.792 --> 36:21.667
SHOTS FIRED.
OFFICER DOWN,
POSSIBLY DEAD.

36:21.667 --> 36:23.667
OH, MY GOD.

36:23.667 --> 36:25.166
HE'S BARELY GOT
A PULSE.

36:25.166 --> 36:28.166
WHAT, DO YOU HAVE
AN OPEN MARRIAGE,

36:28.166 --> 36:29.291
OR IS IT ALL JUST PRETEND
FROM THE BEGINNING?

36:29.291 --> 36:32.667
I'M SURE THIS ISN'T
ABOUT OUR MARRIAGE.

36:32.667 --> 36:33.792
BUT I'M THE LAST PERSON

36:33.792 --> 36:36.041
YOU'RE GONNA SPEAK TO
ON THIS EARTH, SO...

36:36.041 --> 36:38.667
MIGHT AS WELL
TELL ME EVERYTHING.

36:38.667 --> 36:39.333
HE'LL HUNT YOU DOWN.

36:39.333 --> 36:41.208
HE MIGHT HUNT YOU  DOWN.

36:41.208 --> 36:43.750
YOU JUST BECAME
A SECURITY RISK.

36:43.750 --> 36:46.500
YOU KNOW, THEY TOOK OUT JFK
OVER THE PRICE OF OIL,

36:46.500 --> 36:50.041
SO I'D SAY YOUR CHANCES
OF BEING A MILITARY TARGET

36:50.041 --> 36:52.291
ARE PRETTY HIGH.

36:52.291 --> 36:54.583
PFFT. LIKE YOU SAID,
THE STAKES ARE HIGH.

36:54.583 --> 36:57.083
IT'S ALL MORE IMPORTANT
THAN AN INDIVIDUAL.

36:57.083 --> 36:58.041
AM I RIGHT?

36:58.041 --> 37:00.458
IS THAT WHAT YOU TELL
YOURSELF EVERY DAY?

37:00.458 --> 37:01.709
"I'M ONLY A COG

37:01.709 --> 37:05.458
IN THE GREAT WHEEL
OF MISFORTUNE."

37:05.458 --> 37:06.959
JUST THE WAY IT IS.

37:06.959 --> 37:09.709
HOW'D YOU END UP HERE?

37:10.875 --> 37:13.500
HOW THE FUCK
DID THAT HAPPEN?

37:13.500 --> 37:16.375
LOOK. I CAN MAKE A DEAL
OR BREAK ONE.

37:16.375 --> 37:17.333
I HAVE MY OWN CONNECTIONS.

37:17.333 --> 37:20.125
LET'S GET BACK TO
YOUR LITTLE THEATER GIG,

37:20.125 --> 37:22.208
BACKSTAGE
EVERY THURSDAY.

37:22.208 --> 37:25.917
BODYGUARDS OFF LIMITS,
OF COURSE.

37:27.166 --> 37:29.208
DO YOU PRETEND
IT'S...PASSION,

37:29.208 --> 37:33.250
OR IS IT LIKE
TAKING PROZAC?

37:33.250 --> 37:35.667
LEAVE RUSSELL
OUT OF THIS.

37:37.417 --> 37:39.250
[BEEPING]

37:39.250 --> 37:42.417
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

37:42.417 --> 37:43.625
HE HAD BETTER BE DEAD,

37:43.625 --> 37:45.208
OR I SWEAR TO GOD
I'M GONNA KILL HIM.

37:45.208 --> 37:47.041
CALL HIS PUBLICIST.

37:47.041 --> 37:48.083
SHE'LL KNOW
WHERE HE'S HIDING.

37:48.083 --> 37:50.875
Rex: YOU'RE ON, FOLKS.

37:51.250 --> 37:52.375
[APPLAUSE]

37:55.709 --> 37:58.208
NAME YOUR TERMS, JOE.

37:59.875 --> 38:02.500
THIS IS ABOUT DIGNITY.

38:02.500 --> 38:05.333
MY DAUGHTER'S DEATH
ROBBED HER OF HERS,

38:05.333 --> 38:06.333
AND YOU'RE GOING
TO DREDGE UP

38:06.333 --> 38:09.500
WHATEVER LITTLE NOBILITY
YOU HAVE LEFT...

38:09.500 --> 38:12.166
AND GIVE THE WORLD
A LITTLE...

38:12.166 --> 38:14.125
OF WHAT SHE HAD.

38:15.959 --> 38:18.417
I CAN'T BELIEVE
SHE'D WANT THIS.

38:20.417 --> 38:21.542
SHE WAS A FIGHTER.

38:24.041 --> 38:26.500
AND LIKE YOU...

38:27.792 --> 38:28.458
I WASN'T.

38:28.458 --> 38:31.875
SO I HAD TO MAKE
A CHOICE.

38:33.625 --> 38:35.792
JUMP OUT THE WINDOW...

38:35.792 --> 38:38.375
OR LIVE BY THE RULES
THAT SHE DIED BY.

38:38.375 --> 38:39.625
WHAT HAPPENED
TO HER?

38:42.417 --> 38:44.208
A BOY AT HER SCHOOL...

38:44.208 --> 38:46.500
ARMED AND FUCKED UP.

38:47.875 --> 38:50.041
HEADLINES THAT MAKE
EVERY MOMMY AND DADDY
IN AMERICA

38:50.041 --> 38:52.417
CROSS THEIR FINGERS.

38:52.417 --> 38:56.208
"AH, BUT FOR THE GRACE
OF GOD GO I."

39:00.166 --> 39:02.583
SO...

39:02.583 --> 39:05.500
NOW I'M USING THE SAME RIGHT
TO BEAR ARMS HE HAD.

39:05.500 --> 39:10.458
IT'S AN ALL-IN PACKAGE,
I WAS TOLD.

39:10.458 --> 39:11.333
AND YOU...

39:11.333 --> 39:14.583
YOU CAN'T FUCK
WITH FREEDOM...

39:14.583 --> 39:17.959
TO QUOTE A PHRASE.

39:17.959 --> 39:19.333
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

39:19.333 --> 39:21.792
WHAT? YOUR FATHER'S
LAST WORDS?

39:21.792 --> 39:23.625
OHH.

39:23.625 --> 39:24.709
BRILLIANT.

39:24.709 --> 39:27.500
BRILLIANT WAY TO
GO OUT, I THOUGHT.

39:27.500 --> 39:29.500
FACT IS...

39:29.500 --> 39:33.000
IT WAS WHAT
MADE ME CHOOSE YOU
AS THE SPOKESPERSON.

39:33.000 --> 39:34.625
NOBODY KNEW
WHAT MY DAD'S NOTE SAID.

39:39.291 --> 39:40.834
JUST FUCKING SHOOT ME!

39:40.834 --> 39:41.792
GET IT OVER WITH!

39:41.792 --> 39:43.542
I'M SICK
OF YOUR BULLSHIT!

39:55.375 --> 39:58.333
HOW DO YOU KNOW
SO MUCH ABOUT ME?

39:58.333 --> 39:59.959
I'M GOOD WITH DETAILS.

39:59.959 --> 40:02.750
NOBODY KNEW WHAT
WAS IN THAT NOTE, JOE.

40:02.750 --> 40:03.375
ONLY THE COPS.

40:03.375 --> 40:05.417
IT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.

40:05.417 --> 40:06.542
THE FILES ARE FILED.

40:08.375 --> 40:10.875
UNLESS YOU'RE A COP.
IS THAT IT?

40:11.834 --> 40:13.667
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
YOU SHOULD DO THIS?

40:13.667 --> 40:16.041
YOU DON'T HAVE KIDS,
SO YOU DON'T KNOW.

40:19.041 --> 40:25.000
♪ GOD BLESS AMERICA ♪

40:25.000 --> 40:26.375
JUST GIVE US A MINUTE.
STAY THERE.

40:26.375 --> 40:27.250
♪ ...THAT I LOVE ♪

40:27.250 --> 40:29.250
WHAT DO YOU
MAKE OF THAT?

40:29.250 --> 40:32.083
♪ STAND BESIDE HER ♪

40:32.083 --> 40:33.417
♪ AND GUIDE HER ♪
PSYCH WARD.

40:33.417 --> 40:35.208
Pritchard:
SHE MAY HAVE
SEEN SOMETHING.

40:35.208 --> 40:36.333
I'LL CHECK IT OUT.

40:36.333 --> 40:39.041
♪ ...WITH THE LIGHT
FROM ABOVE ♪

40:39.583 --> 40:40.709
HEY, GET BACK HERE!

40:44.625 --> 40:46.250
I DON'T WANT THEM
GETTING ANY CLOSER.

40:46.250 --> 40:47.917
WHAT DO YOU
GOT YOUR HANDS
IN THE AIR FOR?

40:47.917 --> 40:49.667
DON'T COME ANY CLOSER!

40:49.667 --> 40:51.083
MMM...

40:51.083 --> 40:52.250
LOOKS LIKE YOUR HUSBAND

40:52.250 --> 40:55.125
SENT SOME GOONS TO PROTECT YOU
AND YOUR RELATIONSHIPS.

40:55.125 --> 40:56.417
THERE'S WASHINGTON,
THE MIDDLE EAST,

40:56.417 --> 41:00.375
THE MAYOR'S OFFICE,
THE POLICE, THE MOB.

41:00.375 --> 41:03.375
OOH. YOU GUYS WORK
ON ALL SIDES OF THE FENCE.

41:03.375 --> 41:05.959
IT MUST BE HARD
TO KEEP TRACK.

41:05.959 --> 41:07.083
YOU SEE WHAT HAPPENED
OVER THERE?

41:07.083 --> 41:09.083
SO THIS IS REALLY
ABOUT VICTOR.

41:09.083 --> 41:09.834
Joe: YOU'RE
THE PACKAGE.

41:09.834 --> 41:11.792
WHAT?

41:11.792 --> 41:14.750
NOW IT'S TIME TO MAKE
YOUR DEAL WITH GOD.

41:14.750 --> 41:16.458
YOU ALL RIGHT?
Joe: SAY NO.

41:16.458 --> 41:17.500
NO.
HIS WALKIE SIGNAL

41:17.500 --> 41:19.125
IS A BAD THING FOR SENSITIVE
EXPLOSIVE DETONATORS.

41:19.125 --> 41:21.583
GET BACK!

41:21.583 --> 41:22.834
GET BACK!

41:22.834 --> 41:23.875
THERE'S A BOMB
IN HERE.

41:23.875 --> 41:24.834
DID SHE SAY "BOMB?"

41:24.834 --> 41:27.250
Man: WHAT'S UP?
[LAUGHS]

41:29.834 --> 41:30.792
NOW WHAT?

41:30.792 --> 41:34.709
THANK YOU FOR GETTING
THE BALL ROLLING...

41:34.709 --> 41:39.083
BUT IMPROVISE AGAIN
AND EVERYTHING GOES BOOM.

41:44.709 --> 41:46.000
SHE SAID
THERE'S A BOMB.

41:46.000 --> 41:49.000
LET'S CALL
THE HENRY GUYS
JUST IN CASE.

41:49.000 --> 41:51.500
DISPATCH 11, 19 A-6.
REQUEST HENRY UNIT.

41:51.500 --> 41:54.208
GET TO THE ALLEY OF TENTH
AND GRACE ASAP.

41:54.208 --> 41:56.500
YIELD TRAFFIC BETWEEN
SEVENTH AND 12th,
OLIVE AND MAIN.

41:56.500 --> 41:57.458
Dispatcher: HENRY
UNIT ON ITS WAY.

41:57.458 --> 41:59.500
IT'S GANG TURF.
IT COULD BE SOMETHING

41:59.500 --> 42:02.250
HE STUCK HIS NOSE INTO.

42:02.250 --> 42:04.166
Dispatcher: RTO 19-A-6.
HENRY CAR RETURNING,

42:04.166 --> 42:07.166
CODE 3, RESPONDING FROM
VALENCIA TO DOWNTOWN.

42:07.166 --> 42:09.083
Miller: I COPY, DISPATCH.
SHOULD WE CLEAR THE AREA?

42:09.083 --> 42:11.667
Dispatcher: 19-A-6,
STAY WITH OFFICER.

42:11.667 --> 42:12.333
WAIT FOR "H" UNIT
AND SUPERVISOR.

42:12.333 --> 42:14.083
PARAMEDICS ETA 7 MINUTES.

42:14.083 --> 42:16.667
Miller: COPY.

42:16.667 --> 42:17.875
SO, GENTLEMEN,
YOU'VE A BIT

42:17.875 --> 42:18.875
OF A GRIZZLY
SITUATION HERE.

42:18.875 --> 42:20.917
BILL, YOU'RE HERE EARLY.

42:20.917 --> 42:22.083
GIVE US SOME SPACE,
ALL RIGHT?

42:22.083 --> 42:23.000
YEAH, WELL, YOU KNOW,

42:23.000 --> 42:24.166
I'M ALWAYS ON THE HUNT
FOR THAT EMMY.

42:24.166 --> 42:25.291
YEAH. HEY, LOOK,
WE GOT NOTHIN'
FOR YOU YET.

42:25.291 --> 42:28.375
THE FAMILY HASN'T
BEEN INFORMED,
SO NO NAMES YET.

42:28.375 --> 42:29.208
WHAT HAPPENED?

42:29.208 --> 42:31.542
BILL, WE'VE BEEN HERE
5 MINUTES, OK?

42:31.542 --> 42:33.583
JUST BACK OFF.
YOU'LL BE THE FIRST
TO KNOW, I PROMISE.

42:33.583 --> 42:34.709
OK, YEAH. PROMISES,
PROMISES.

42:34.709 --> 42:36.834
Dispatcher: ONE ADAM 97
RESPOND, PLEASE.

42:36.834 --> 42:40.709
[CELL PHONE RINGS]
ONE ADAM 97, PLEASE RESPOND.

42:40.709 --> 42:41.709
BILL TOLLMAN.

42:41.709 --> 42:43.458
LOOK AT THE HOT DOG STAND.

42:43.458 --> 42:45.375
SHE CAN TELL YOU THE STORY.

42:45.375 --> 42:48.542
NO CAMERAS YET.

42:48.542 --> 42:49.792
STAY ON THE PHONE.

42:49.792 --> 42:51.125
Bill: WELL, I WANNA
KNOW WHO YOU ARE

42:51.125 --> 42:52.709
BEFORE
I GET ANY DEEPER
INTO THIS THING.

42:52.709 --> 42:55.792
YOU WERE HAPPY TO GET A TIP
20 MINUTES AGO.

42:55.792 --> 43:00.166
WHY ALL OF A SUDDEN
A CHANGE OF HEART?

43:00.166 --> 43:01.166
Bill: BECAUSE
A COP IS DOWN.

43:01.166 --> 43:03.542
AND YOU CAN HELP.

43:03.542 --> 43:05.542
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
I'LL LET HER TALK TO.

43:05.542 --> 43:07.125
SHE SAW IT ALL.

43:07.125 --> 43:13.417
Dispatcher: ONE ADAM 18,
ALAMEDA AND 11th,
ETA 12 MINUTES...

43:13.417 --> 43:15.250
BILL! HEY, BILL!
JESUS CHRIST.

43:15.250 --> 43:17.000
BILL,
GET BACK HERE!

43:17.000 --> 43:18.542
THE BOMB SQUAD'S
ON THE WAY.

43:18.542 --> 43:19.542
I GOT A GUY
ON THE CELL PHONE
TELLS ME

43:19.542 --> 43:21.333
SHE'S GOT
THE WHOLE STORY.

43:21.333 --> 43:22.500
SON OF A BITCH.

43:22.500 --> 43:23.625
WAIT TILL
HE GETS BACK.
NO ONE--

43:23.625 --> 43:25.250
NOT YOU,
NOT US--
GOES OVER THERE.

43:25.250 --> 43:26.834
I SWEAR TO GOD,
I'LL TAKE YOU
DOWN, BILL.

43:26.834 --> 43:28.208
NOW GET
BACK HERE!

43:41.959 --> 43:44.250
Joe: WELCOME TO OUR PARTY.
WE'RE CONFERENCED.

43:44.250 --> 43:47.792
A TEAM. LIBERTY WALLACE,

43:47.792 --> 43:51.166
PLEASE LET ME INTRODUCE YOU
TO BILL TOLLMAN.

43:51.166 --> 43:53.291
WE'RE LUCKY
TO HAVE BILL JOIN US.

43:53.291 --> 43:58.625
HE'S AMBITIOUS, SMART,
AND FOR THE MOST PART, HONEST.

43:58.625 --> 43:59.125
I'M SORRY.

43:59.125 --> 44:01.166
AND YOU ARE?

44:01.166 --> 44:02.500
Joe: I'M JOE.
I'M OUT FOR VENGEANCE.

44:02.500 --> 44:05.709
LIBERTY NEEDS FORGIVENESS,

44:05.709 --> 44:07.083
AND WE BOTH NEED PUBLICITY.

44:07.083 --> 44:08.458
WHY ME?

44:08.458 --> 44:10.291
YOUR LUCKY DAY.

44:10.291 --> 44:12.875
WHY DON'T YOU BRING HIM
UP TO SPEED, LIBERTY?

44:12.875 --> 44:15.333
HE'S GOT A MILITARY
ISSUE SNIPER RIFLE
POINTED RIGHT AT YOU.

44:15.333 --> 44:18.041
HE'S AN EXCELLENT SHOT.

44:19.875 --> 44:21.625
THERE'S A BOMB
IN THE HOT DOG CART.

44:21.625 --> 44:24.417
IT'S SET TO BLOW
IF MY CELL PHONE BATTERY
DIES FOR ANY REASON.

44:24.417 --> 44:27.083
THE BOMB'S
BIG ENOUGH TO BLOW UP
THIS ENTIRE BLOCK.

44:27.083 --> 44:28.458
THINK OKLAHOMA.

44:28.458 --> 44:30.500
THAT THEATER'S
GONNA LET OUT
IN LESS THAN AN HOUR.

44:30.500 --> 44:32.542
I HAVE LESS THAN AN HOUR
LEFT ON MY BATTERY.

44:34.333 --> 44:37.834
LOOK. I DIE EITHER WAY.

44:37.834 --> 44:40.709
UNLESS YOU GET OUT
OF HERE, SO DO YOU.

44:40.709 --> 44:43.709
AREN'T YOU LIBERTY WALLACE
OF, UM...

44:43.709 --> 44:44.333
YES.

44:44.333 --> 44:47.125
ANY DEMANDS?

44:48.291 --> 44:51.333
HE WANTS...

44:53.291 --> 44:56.500
UM...

44:56.500 --> 45:00.583
HE WANTS SOMEBODY
TO PAY FOR THE DEATH
OF HIS DAUGHTER.

45:00.583 --> 45:00.917
Joe: ALMOST RIGHT.

45:05.875 --> 45:09.333
JOE'S DAUGHTER DIED
FROM A FUCKED UP
KID WITH A GUN...

45:09.333 --> 45:11.834
AND, UH...

45:11.834 --> 45:16.000
IT WAS
A GUN MANUFACTURED
BY MY COMPANY.

45:16.000 --> 45:20.208
HE WANTS ME TO DIE
KNOWING I HAVE
BLOOD ON MY HANDS.

45:21.208 --> 45:23.041
JOE...

45:23.041 --> 45:25.834
YOU GOTTA RETHINK HERE.
THIS IS CRAZY.

45:25.834 --> 45:28.000
BILL, THERE'S A REAL GUN
POINTED AT YOU.

45:28.000 --> 45:31.125
WHAT I MEAN IS,
THERE ARE OTHER WAYS.

45:31.125 --> 45:34.375
MM-HMM. WELL, THAT'S WHERE
YOU COME IN, BILL.

45:34.375 --> 45:38.208
SO YOU WANT ME TO USE MY
INFLUENCE AS A JOURNALIST

45:38.208 --> 45:40.709
TO DEBATE THE RIGHT
TO BEAR ARMS WITH YOU

45:40.709 --> 45:42.834
BECAUSE YOU'VE GOT
A GUN POINTED AT ME,

45:42.834 --> 45:44.834
AND I'M STANDING
NEXT TO A BOMB

45:44.834 --> 45:46.291
THAT'S ON
FINAL COUNTDOWN?

45:46.291 --> 45:47.792
YEAH.

45:48.834 --> 45:51.709
AND WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN ALL THIS IS OVER?

45:51.709 --> 45:54.792
I BLOW MY BRAINS OUT.

45:54.792 --> 45:58.208
SO THIS BECOMES
MY JOURNALISTIC
MOMENT OF TRUTH?

45:58.208 --> 46:01.000
YOUR EMMY...

46:01.000 --> 46:02.542
AND YOUR QUEST.

46:02.542 --> 46:05.041
I'M SORRY, JOE.
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO SAY HERE?

46:05.041 --> 46:06.458
SAY YES.

46:06.458 --> 46:10.000
NO. SAY THAT
YOU'RE ACCOUNTABLE.

46:10.000 --> 46:11.834
SAY YES.

46:14.083 --> 46:16.208
THERE ARE PLENTY
OF CAUSES, JOE.

46:17.583 --> 46:20.750
Joe: BILL, LOOK AT LIBERTY.

46:20.750 --> 46:22.750
SHE'S GOING TO DIE.

46:22.750 --> 46:25.959
IT'S HER CHOICE WHEN.
IT'S MY CHOICE HOW.

46:25.959 --> 46:27.417
YOU HAVE A SIMILAR DILEMMA.

46:27.417 --> 46:30.667
NOW LOOK AROUND.

46:31.250 --> 46:33.333
[GASPS]

46:33.333 --> 46:37.291
JESUS. SHIT. HE--OOH.

46:37.291 --> 46:38.875
HE SHOT ME.

46:38.875 --> 46:41.291
ALL RIGHT. I'LL DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

46:41.291 --> 46:42.792
Joe: HE'S GOING TO DIE
IN YOUR ARMS, LIBERTY.

46:42.792 --> 46:43.875
JUST HANG ON.
GET READY.

46:43.875 --> 46:49.125
WATCHING SOMEONE DIE
CHANGES YOU FOREVER.

46:49.125 --> 46:50.583
SHH.

46:50.583 --> 46:52.709
[GRUNTS]

46:52.709 --> 46:54.875
Dispatcher:
19-A-6 TO DISPATCH.

46:54.875 --> 46:56.959
WE HAVE A FEMALE
WITH A GUN.

46:56.959 --> 46:59.333
I'M NOT DYING.

46:59.333 --> 47:00.875
Joe: HIS FATHER
IS SENATOR ROBERT TOLLMAN.

47:00.875 --> 47:04.125
HE'S ALSO
A CONSTITUTIONAL LAWYER.

47:04.125 --> 47:05.291
HE LOBBIED FOR THE NRA,

47:05.291 --> 47:08.625
SO WE KNOW WHICH SIDE
HIS BREAD IS BUTTERED ON.

47:08.625 --> 47:11.458
HE'S PROUD OF HIS SON...

47:11.458 --> 47:16.333
AND NOW, LIKE ME, HAS EVERY
REASON TO SWITCH SIDES.

47:16.333 --> 47:20.125
HEY.
OK. UNH. OK. OK.

47:20.125 --> 47:21.959
HEY, HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?

47:21.959 --> 47:23.458
TURN THAT FUCKING
THING OFF. I TOLD YOU.

47:23.458 --> 47:27.000
OK. OH.

47:27.000 --> 47:31.125
JUST HANG ON.
HELP'S COMING.

47:31.125 --> 47:32.750
NO, IT'S NOT.

47:32.750 --> 47:33.709
FUCKING ASSHOLE.

47:33.709 --> 47:36.083
SUE ME!
GET HIM OUTTA HERE!

47:41.750 --> 47:44.291
OOH, CAN'T BUY
THIS KIND OF PRESS.

47:44.291 --> 47:45.250
10:00 NEWS, BUDDY.

47:45.250 --> 47:45.834
BACK IT UP. BACK IT UP.

47:45.834 --> 47:49.333
CALL MY FATHER FOR ME.

47:49.333 --> 47:52.709
HUH?

47:52.709 --> 47:56.000
[GURGLES]

47:58.000 --> 47:59.000
AH.

48:02.709 --> 48:03.000
AH.

48:05.750 --> 48:07.041
[CRIES]

48:19.750 --> 48:23.333
WHY ARE YOU
DOING THIS?

48:23.333 --> 48:27.166
WHY?! WHY ARE
YOU DOING THIS?!

48:27.166 --> 48:28.208
TELL ME!

48:29.667 --> 48:31.875
YOUR DICK IS THE SIZE
OF THE LITTLE TRIGGER
ON THAT GUN!

48:31.875 --> 48:34.250
THAT MAKES YOU
NOTHING, JOE!

48:34.250 --> 48:37.333
YOU'RE LESS
THAN NOTHING!

48:37.333 --> 48:39.208
YOU PROBABLY DIDN'T
EVEN HAVE A DAUGHTER.

48:39.208 --> 48:41.125
IF YOU DID,
SHE'S BETTER OFF DEAD.

48:44.875 --> 48:48.125
I'LL...
FORGIVE YOU FOR THAT...

48:51.250 --> 48:52.959
GIVEN THE CIRCUMSTANCES.

48:52.959 --> 48:54.250
[GUNSHOT]

48:54.250 --> 48:55.333
JUST KILL ME!

48:55.333 --> 48:56.709
GET IT OVER WITH!
SHUT UP.

48:56.709 --> 48:57.917
I'M NOT
THE ONE SHOOTING.

48:57.917 --> 48:59.125
I CAN'T TAKE ANY MORE.

49:02.625 --> 49:03.250
I'LL HANG UP.

49:09.750 --> 49:11.625
Joe: THAT ASSHOLE'S
SHOOTING WITH A 9 MM.,

49:11.625 --> 49:13.083
SO HE HASN'T GOT A HOPE

49:13.083 --> 49:14.041
OF HITTING YOU
FROM THAT DISTANCE.

49:17.583 --> 49:19.959
AH, VICTOR.
YOU HAVE MADE MY DAY.

49:19.959 --> 49:22.750
HELLO.

49:32.125 --> 49:33.750
Joe: IT'S KINDA IRONIC.

49:33.750 --> 49:36.625
ME SAVING YOUR LIFE.

49:37.959 --> 49:41.333
[SIRENS APPROACH]

49:44.083 --> 49:46.166
THEY'RE HERE.

50:03.458 --> 50:05.834
THE OFFICER
WENT DOWN THERE.

50:05.834 --> 50:08.208
THE LADY WITH THE BOMB
IS ACROSS THE STREET.

50:11.125 --> 50:12.250
Joe: IT'S TIME
TO DO SOMETHING.

50:12.250 --> 50:14.625
BILL HAS A TAPE RECORDER
IN HIS SUIT POCKET.

50:14.625 --> 50:17.875
NAME NAMES, LIBERTY.

50:17.875 --> 50:19.333
BLOW THE LOBBIES WIDE OPEN.

50:19.333 --> 50:20.834
PAYOFFS ARE ALWAYS GOOD
NEWSMAKERS.

50:20.834 --> 50:23.125
SHIT. YOU'RE
AN AMATEUR, JOE.

50:23.125 --> 50:25.458
NOW DON'T TELL ME THAT
YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT
THE FALLOUT.

50:25.458 --> 50:27.500
YOUR HUSBAND OR SOMEONE
HE WORKS FOR

50:27.500 --> 50:30.500
HAS ORDERED THE CIA THUGS
TO PUT A BULLET IN YOU.

50:30.500 --> 50:31.375
IS THAT THE WORLD
YOU WANNA LIVE IN?

50:31.375 --> 50:33.291
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU CAN ACCOMPLISH

50:33.291 --> 50:36.333
BY ME BABBLING
ABOUT SENATOR THIS
AND SENATOR THAT?

50:36.333 --> 50:36.750
THAT'S NOT GONNA
DO ANYTHING.

50:36.750 --> 50:39.041
IT'S A START.

50:39.041 --> 50:41.792
IT'S AN END, JOE.

50:41.792 --> 50:44.709
LET ME DO WHAT
I CAN REALLY DO.

50:44.709 --> 50:46.625
LET ME WORK
FROM THE INSIDE.

50:46.625 --> 50:48.709
I CAN--I CAN...

50:48.709 --> 50:51.542
I CAN DO SOMETHING.

50:51.542 --> 50:54.542
OH, SO THAT'S WHAT YOU TELL
YOURSELF EVERY MORNING?

50:54.542 --> 50:55.959
JOE, I CAN REALLY
CHANGE THINGS.

50:55.959 --> 50:57.709
I PROMISE YOU
I'LL DO IT.

50:57.709 --> 51:01.625
I PROMISE.

51:01.625 --> 51:02.917
AAH!

51:10.208 --> 51:12.834
POLICE! PUT 'EM DOWN!

51:12.834 --> 51:14.500
COME ON.

51:15.875 --> 51:17.625
COME ON.

51:18.959 --> 51:23.709
WE CAN ALWAYS COUNT
ON OUR NATION'S FINEST
TO SERVE AND PROTECT.

51:23.709 --> 51:25.709
Officer over scanner:
SHOT FIRED. I'VE GOT
A CIVILIAN DOWN,

51:25.709 --> 51:27.750
POSSIBLY DEAD.
LOOKS LIKE A SHOOTER.

51:43.208 --> 51:47.208
SENATOR LIBBY
TOOK AT LEAST
3 PAYMENTS IN CASH.

51:47.208 --> 51:49.917
SENATOR LIPTON KRICK,
CONGRESSMAN GOMEZ...

51:49.917 --> 51:53.083
CHECK GENEVA
BANK ACCOUNT,

51:53.083 --> 51:54.750
SWISS UNION
BANK ACCOUNTS,

51:54.750 --> 51:58.500
CAYMAN ISLANDS, BAHAMAS.
MY HUSBAND...

51:58.500 --> 52:00.500
VICTOR WALLACE
IS FUCKING

52:00.500 --> 52:03.208
THE PRESIDENT'S WIFE,
AMONG OTHERS.

52:03.208 --> 52:05.792
PRESIDENTS OR WIVES?

52:08.458 --> 52:09.917
Liberty: WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

52:09.917 --> 52:12.041
NOTHING. YOU'RE ON A ROLL.
KEEP IT GOIN'.

52:12.041 --> 52:15.375
YOU'RE ALREADY ON THE NEWS.

52:15.375 --> 52:18.625
YOU KNOW, VICTOR'S
MOBILIZED EVERY SENATOR
I JUST MENTIONED.

52:18.625 --> 52:21.125
THE POLICE CHIEF
IS IN HIS BACK POCKET.

52:21.125 --> 52:22.417
HE SUPPLIES THE GANG

52:22.417 --> 52:25.083
THAT CONTROLS
THIS CORNER,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

52:27.500 --> 52:29.000
Joe: HE?

52:29.000 --> 52:32.917
OK, I. WE.

52:32.917 --> 52:35.291
I. I'M IN THIS, OK?

52:35.291 --> 52:37.750
IS THAT WHAT
YOU WANT ME TO SAY?
I'M IN IT.

52:37.750 --> 52:42.458
YES...

52:42.458 --> 52:44.375
NOW WHO
YOU GONNA TRUST?

52:44.375 --> 52:46.667
NOBODY.

52:46.667 --> 52:47.875
KEEP TALKING.

52:47.875 --> 52:51.166
NO. I'LL NAME NAMES.

52:51.166 --> 52:52.458
I'LL BURY EVERYONE
WHO DESERVES IT,

52:52.458 --> 52:54.500
BUT YOU HAVE TO SHUT
THIS BOMB OFF.

52:54.500 --> 52:56.959
NAH, I CAN'T.

52:56.959 --> 52:58.667
THEN I CAN'T.

52:58.667 --> 53:00.000
Joe: THAT'S FAIR ENOUGH.

53:00.000 --> 53:01.959
YOU'VE DONE
YOUR JOB ANYWAY.

53:01.959 --> 53:04.458
NOW WE CAN DEPEND
ON BILL'S DAD THE SENATOR

53:04.458 --> 53:06.417
IN HIS NEWFOUND QUEST.

53:06.417 --> 53:10.125
HE'LL GO DOWN
AS A HERO FOR THE CAUSE.

53:10.125 --> 53:16.625
IT WAS A LIFE WELL SPENT
IN THE BIG PICTURE.

53:27.083 --> 53:30.000
HAVE A HOT DOG.

53:30.000 --> 53:31.834
YOU DON'T WANNA GO OUT
ON AN EMPTY STOMACH.

53:31.834 --> 53:33.709
LET THEM TAKE HIM AWAY.

54:01.625 --> 54:02.875
OVER HERE.

54:02.875 --> 54:04.500
May: EVERY THURSDAY
THEY MEET BACKSTAGE,

54:04.500 --> 54:07.917
GO INTO RUSSELL'S
DRESSING ROOM,
AND LOCK THE DOOR.

54:07.917 --> 54:09.542
THEY ORDER IN.

54:10.959 --> 54:12.667
[BEEPS]

54:14.333 --> 54:16.709
BASTARD CHANGED
THE LOCK. FUCK!

54:16.709 --> 54:19.000
[BEEPS]

54:21.291 --> 54:24.250
May: YEAH, SHE SLINKS OUT
SOMETIME DURING THE NIGHT,

54:24.250 --> 54:27.959
AND WE DON'T SEE
RUSSELL AGAIN UNTIL
THE NEXT PERFORMANCE.

54:29.208 --> 54:30.375
[BEEPING]

54:36.959 --> 54:39.667
OH, EXCEPT FOR TONIGHT.

54:39.667 --> 54:41.917
HE'S PROBABLY IN THERE
FUCKED TO DEATH.

54:41.917 --> 54:44.041
UH-OH. TIME TO CALL
A LOCKSMITH.

54:44.041 --> 54:46.458
BACKUP'S COMIN' IN FROM 53.

54:46.458 --> 54:49.250
LOOKS LIKE WE'VE GOT
OURSELVES A SNIPER.

54:49.250 --> 54:50.917
NOW THERE'S NO I.D.
ON THE WOMAN

54:50.917 --> 54:52.542
AND NO TRACE
ON HER CELL PHONE YET.

54:52.542 --> 54:53.750
IF SHE'S CHAINED
TO THE STAND,

54:53.750 --> 54:55.333
SHE TOLD OFFICERS
THAT THERE'S A BOMB,
ALL RIGHT?

54:55.333 --> 54:57.291
WE BELIEVE SHE'S WORKING
WITH THE SNIPER.

54:57.291 --> 54:59.458
THE MAN ON THE GROUND
OUT THERE

54:59.458 --> 55:01.125
IS A REPORTER WITH KNBS.

55:01.125 --> 55:02.625
BILL TOLLMAN,
THE SENATOR'S SON...

55:02.625 --> 55:04.250
THAT KNBS...
WE BELIEVE SHOT.

55:04.250 --> 55:06.041
WE HAVE
A CONFIRMED FATALITY

55:06.041 --> 55:07.208
IN THE PARKING STRUCTURE
BACK HERE.

55:07.208 --> 55:09.000
WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH
INFORMATION ON THAT YET,

55:09.000 --> 55:10.792
BUT WE CAN'T RULE OUT
TERRORISTS, MILITIA,

55:10.792 --> 55:12.458
OR JUST YOUR BASIC NUT CASE.

55:12.458 --> 55:15.041
NOW WE'RE GONNA BLOCK
FROM FIFTH TO TENTH
ALL UP TO BERRY.

55:15.041 --> 55:17.291
NOW WE'VE GOT AT LEAST
20 BUILDINGS TO EVACUATE,

55:17.291 --> 55:18.583
AND WE'RE THIN ON MANPOWER,

55:18.583 --> 55:20.959
SO USE, UH, UNIFORMS
TO BACK YOU UP.

55:20.959 --> 55:21.917
ALL RIGHT?
BE SAFE, GENTLEMEN.

55:21.917 --> 55:23.333
THANK YOU. LET'S GO.

55:25.792 --> 55:27.667
Mac: CAPTAIN,

55:27.667 --> 55:29.625
WE GOT NO LOCATION
ON THE SHOOTER,

55:29.625 --> 55:31.291
NO I.D. ON THE WOMAN.
WE GOT BACKUP COMING,

55:31.291 --> 55:33.458
AND WE'RE SET UP
IN THE GARAGE BACK THERE.

55:33.458 --> 55:37.083
WOULD SOMEBODY
SHUT THEM DOWN?! JESUS!

55:37.083 --> 55:39.333
CLEAR THE MEDIA
BACK, PLEASE.

55:42.709 --> 55:45.458
WE ARE LIVE.

55:47.500 --> 55:48.667
THE DRAMA CONTINUES
IN DOWNTOWN L.A.,

55:48.667 --> 55:52.208
WHERE WE APPARENTLY
HAVE A FATAL SHOOTING
OF AN OFFICER,

55:52.208 --> 55:53.500
HERE AT THE CORNER
OF GRACE AND NINTH.

55:53.500 --> 55:55.000
Liberty: IS YOUR WIFE
GOING TO BE TUNING IN?

55:55.000 --> 55:56.625
HA HA. NO.

55:56.625 --> 55:59.000
BUT I GUARANTEE
YOUR HUSBAND'S WATCHING.

55:59.000 --> 56:00.208
BACK TO YOU, DENNIS.

56:00.208 --> 56:04.500
[LAUGHS] MY HUSBAND.

56:05.709 --> 56:08.500
MY HUSBAND'S ON THE WAY
TO THE AIRPORT BY NOW.

56:08.500 --> 56:12.250
HE WILL BE UNREACHABLE
FOR COMMENT.

56:15.125 --> 56:16.792
WHY'D YOU MARRY HIM?

56:16.792 --> 56:19.834
THOUGHT HE COULD SAVE
MY FATHER'S COMPANY.

56:20.375 --> 56:22.750
IT WAS A BAD IDEA.

56:22.750 --> 56:24.959
I EVEN THOUGHT I LOVED HIM.

56:26.208 --> 56:27.792
GONNA DO A SHIELD RESCUE
FOR THE GUY ON THE GROUND?

56:27.792 --> 56:29.375
NO. IT'S TOO RISKY
TILL WE FIND OUT
WHERE THE SHOOTER IS.

56:29.375 --> 56:33.375
POOR BASTARD'S
GOING TO BLEED OUT.

56:33.375 --> 56:36.834
I WANT ALL TRAFFIC
LOCKED DOWN FROM
FIFTH TO NINTH.

56:36.834 --> 56:38.083
YEAH, IT'S DONE ALREADY.

56:38.083 --> 56:40.875
GOOD. WHO'S
THE NEGOTIATOR ON CALL?

56:40.875 --> 56:42.083
DOCTOR WILL BE HERE
IN 10 MINUTES, CAPTAIN.

56:42.083 --> 56:43.375
Liberty: JOE, MORE DEATH

56:43.375 --> 56:44.500
ISN'T GOING TO MAKE
THE GUNS DISAPPEAR.

56:44.500 --> 56:46.959
IT'S NOT GOING TO
BRING YOUR DAUGHTER BACK.

56:46.959 --> 56:50.000
LOOK, I'M BEGGING YOU.

56:50.000 --> 56:52.500
OH, LIBERTY.

56:52.500 --> 56:53.834
TIANANMEN SQUARE
BOILED DOWN

56:53.834 --> 56:56.041
TO ONE MAN STANDING
IN FRONT OF A TANK

56:56.041 --> 56:58.375
THAT COULDN'T
MOVE OR SHOOT,

56:58.375 --> 56:59.917
BECAUSE HUMAN DIGNITY

56:59.917 --> 57:01.875
WAS STRONGER THAN
STEEL OR BULLETS.

57:01.875 --> 57:03.083
HE CHANGED A NATION.

57:03.083 --> 57:05.542
THAT WAS A COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT SITUATION.

57:05.542 --> 57:06.166
WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE?

57:06.166 --> 57:08.000
WE GOT GATED
COMMUNITIES,

57:08.000 --> 57:10.000
SECURITY SYSTEMS,

57:10.000 --> 57:11.792
AND KIDS CARRYING
COMBAT WEAPONS,

57:11.792 --> 57:13.500
ALL BECAUSE MOST PEOPLE

57:13.500 --> 57:15.458
HAVEN'T EVEN READ
THE SECOND AMENDMENT.

57:15.458 --> 57:19.166
SO, OUR FREEDOM OF
SPEECH IS PROTECTED

57:19.166 --> 57:21.625
AS LONG AS
WE DON'T PISS OFF
A GUY WITH A GUN.

57:21.625 --> 57:24.333
I'M NOT BRAVE ENOUGH
TO TAKE A BULLET FOR MY COUNTRY.

57:24.333 --> 57:25.959
YOU UNDERESTIMATE
YOURSELF.

57:25.959 --> 57:27.583
THE ONE THING

57:27.583 --> 57:28.458
THAT GUARANTEES
OUR FREEDOM

57:28.458 --> 57:33.166
AND INDEPENDENCE
IS RESPONSIBILITY.

57:33.166 --> 57:34.917
WE LOST THAT
SOMEWHERE BETWEEN

57:34.917 --> 57:38.291
VIETNAM AND PRESIDENTIAL
BLOW JOBS.

57:38.291 --> 57:41.208
MANY OF THE FATHERS OF
THE CONSTITUTION HAD SLAVES,

57:41.208 --> 57:43.458
BUT THEY WROTE
A DOCUMENT...

57:43.458 --> 57:44.125
ABOUT FREEDOM.

57:44.125 --> 57:46.750
[LAUGHS] GO FIGURE.

57:48.250 --> 57:50.875
SO YOU SEE, THINGS
ARE MEANT TO CHANGE.

57:50.875 --> 57:53.250
WE'RE ALL
GROWN UP NOW.

57:53.250 --> 57:55.417
SO ARE YOU, LIBERTY.

57:55.417 --> 57:58.125
I THINK YOU'VE
FIGURED OUT THAT

57:58.125 --> 57:59.709
THERE IS
NO SUCH THING

57:59.709 --> 58:02.625
AS A POLITICALLY
CORRECT GUN.

58:02.625 --> 58:04.500
I'LL SAY ALL THAT
TO THE PRESS.

58:04.500 --> 58:07.125
BUT PLEASE,
TURN THIS BOMB OFF, JOE.

58:07.125 --> 58:10.166
Woman: I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO NEXT.

58:10.166 --> 58:14.000
FEELS LIKE THIS
WHOLE THING WAS A DREAM.

58:14.000 --> 58:16.750
Man: I SHOULD HAVE
TOLD YOU BEFORE, BUT I...

58:16.750 --> 58:19.750
WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

58:19.750 --> 58:22.375
[BEEPING]

58:31.041 --> 58:32.959
[RAPID BEEPING]

58:35.291 --> 58:39.125
[BEEPING SLOWS DOWN]

58:50.500 --> 58:54.166
Joe: HUH.
THE COPS HAVE G-36s.

58:54.166 --> 58:56.000
DID YOU MAKE
THAT DEAL, TOO?

58:56.000 --> 58:57.625
IT WAS MORE
OF A DONATION.

58:57.625 --> 58:59.834
AND I'LL BET
YOU WERE A HERO.

58:59.834 --> 59:02.166
I GOT A BIG LUNCHEON,

59:02.166 --> 59:04.500
KEY TO THE CITY,
MAYOR IN MY POCKET.

59:04.500 --> 59:07.000
YOU MAKE IT SOUND
SO EASY.

59:07.000 --> 59:07.959
WHEN YOU'VE GOT
THE CASH FLOW,

59:07.959 --> 59:09.417
A LITTLE PLANNING
GOES A LONG WAY.

59:09.417 --> 59:10.709
UH, DID THEY KNOW
YOU HAD JUST SOLD

59:10.709 --> 59:12.792
26 STRIPPED DOWN
P-99s

59:12.792 --> 59:14.417
THAT WENT STRAIGHT
TO THE STREET?

59:14.417 --> 59:15.959
I GUESS
IT WAS ONE OF THOSE

59:15.959 --> 59:18.542
"AN EYE FOR AN EYE"
DEALS.

59:18.542 --> 59:21.166
IT'S EASY TO GET
LOST IN THE DEAL.

59:21.166 --> 59:23.834
I KNOW
IT'S NOT AN EXCUSE.

59:24.875 --> 59:27.083
THIS IS A PERFECT
FUCKING NIGHTMARE.

59:27.083 --> 59:30.625
127 LOCATIONS FOR
AN ASSHOLE WITH A GUN.

59:30.625 --> 59:31.542
WE GOT A CELL PHONE
WE CAN'T BUST INTO

59:31.542 --> 59:33.542
AND A BOMB
NEXT TO A THEATER.

59:33.542 --> 59:34.583
ANYBODY PICKING UP
IN THERE YET?

59:34.583 --> 59:35.583
JUST VOICE MAIL, SIR.

59:35.583 --> 59:36.667
FUCKING VOICE MAIL!

59:41.667 --> 59:42.709
OH.

59:42.709 --> 59:45.208
THE SHOOTER IS BACK.

59:45.208 --> 59:47.250
WHO DOES HE WORK FOR,

59:47.250 --> 59:49.000
YOUR HUSBAND
OR THE CIA?

59:49.000 --> 59:52.083
WHOEVER'S GOT THE CASH.

59:52.083 --> 59:52.750
[HELICOPTER APPROACHING]

01:00:05.417 --> 01:00:07.125
WHO'S THE COWBOY
IN THE CHOPPER?

01:00:07.125 --> 01:00:08.875
WELL, GET HIM HIGHER.
HE'S SURVEILLANCE.

01:00:08.875 --> 01:00:10.917
I DON'T WANT HIM LANDING
ON THE FUCKING ROOFTOP.

01:00:14.667 --> 01:00:16.041
Mac: OK, YOU GUYS.
LET'S GET IN THERE.

01:00:16.041 --> 01:00:17.583
LET'S GET INTO THE THEATER.

01:00:17.583 --> 01:00:20.792
Man: I SHOULD HAVE
TOLD YOU BEFORE, BUT I...

01:00:23.375 --> 01:00:24.625
Woman, on stage:
WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

01:00:24.625 --> 01:00:25.917
IT'S UP TO YOU.

01:00:25.917 --> 01:00:28.375
DO YOU STILL LOVE ME?

01:00:29.291 --> 01:00:30.208
OF COURSE I DO.

01:00:30.208 --> 01:00:33.208
HOW ABOUT YOU?

01:00:33.208 --> 01:00:36.166
OF COURSE.

01:00:36.166 --> 01:00:39.125
IT WON'T MAKE
A BIT OF DIFFERENCE.

01:00:40.667 --> 01:00:42.959
[APPLAUSE]

01:00:45.458 --> 01:00:46.750
HOW FULL IS THE THEATER?

01:00:46.750 --> 01:00:48.583
Usher:
IT'S THE LAST PERFORMANCE.

01:00:59.542 --> 01:01:02.166
I FIGURE 10
TO CLEAR THE BUILDING.

01:01:02.166 --> 01:01:04.458
Mac: COPY THAT.
NO ONE EXITS THE FRONT DOOR.

01:01:04.458 --> 01:01:06.375
HOLD UNTIL WE'VE CLEARED
ALL REAR EXITS.

01:01:19.750 --> 01:01:23.000
SENATOR TOLLMAN'S SON
WAS JUST SHOT

01:01:23.000 --> 01:01:25.792
BY THE SAME GUY
WHO'S GOT LIBERTY.

01:01:29.834 --> 01:01:31.875
CALL UP YOUR HUSBAND.

01:01:31.875 --> 01:01:33.458
WHY?

01:01:33.458 --> 01:01:35.000
[CELL PHONE RINGING]

01:01:35.000 --> 01:01:37.875
[RING]

01:01:40.166 --> 01:01:43.041
YEAH?

01:01:43.041 --> 01:01:44.417
Joe: WHO CALLED THE MILITIA?

01:01:44.417 --> 01:01:47.583
I WANT TO TALK
TO LIBERTY.

01:01:47.583 --> 01:01:49.166
TOUCHING.

01:01:49.166 --> 01:01:51.166
SO IT'S NOT
ONE OF YOURS?

01:01:51.166 --> 01:01:52.875
THAT'S NOT GOOD, VICTOR.

01:01:52.875 --> 01:01:54.083
LIBERTY, ARE YOU THERE?

01:01:54.083 --> 01:01:56.834
SUCH A SWEET NAME,
DON'T YOU THINK?

01:01:56.834 --> 01:01:58.583
HER PARENTS
WERE REPUBLICAN.

01:01:58.583 --> 01:02:01.000
I WANT TO TALK
TO MY WIFE.

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:04.041
Liberty: I'M HERE. ALIVE...

01:02:04.041 --> 01:02:06.208
AND ON TV.

01:02:06.208 --> 01:02:07.875
I, UM...

01:02:07.875 --> 01:02:11.792
I KNOW, YOU'RE DOING
WHAT YOU HAVE TO DO.

01:02:15.792 --> 01:02:17.792
DO YOU KNOW
WHO'S CALLING THE SHOTS?

01:02:17.792 --> 01:02:19.667
THE PRESIDENT'S WIFE?

01:02:20.208 --> 01:02:22.458
COME ON.

01:02:23.917 --> 01:02:25.041
NO, OF COURSE NOT.

01:02:25.041 --> 01:02:27.041
IF IT WERE HER,
YOU'D BE STANDING HERE.

01:02:29.375 --> 01:02:31.709
UM...

01:02:31.709 --> 01:02:34.750
I'M--I'M DOING
WHAT I CAN, BUT...

01:02:34.750 --> 01:02:37.417
YOU KNOW THE RULES.
RIGHT?

01:02:37.417 --> 01:02:40.375
AW, HONEY...

01:02:40.375 --> 01:02:41.417
FUCK YOU.

01:02:41.417 --> 01:02:45.041
JOE, HANG UP.

01:02:45.041 --> 01:02:46.208
WELL, WHAT SHE MEANT IS,

01:02:46.208 --> 01:02:49.083
WHY DON'T YOU LET HER
DIE WITH SOME DIGNITY?

01:02:57.417 --> 01:03:00.750
GET THE CAR.
MR. WALLACE IS LEAVING.

01:03:00.750 --> 01:03:02.250
Driver: YES, SIR.

01:03:14.208 --> 01:03:16.000
HOW DO YOU KNOW VICTOR?

01:03:16.000 --> 01:03:16.917
CLASSIFIED.

01:03:19.291 --> 01:03:22.083
Policeman: THIS WAY.
COME ON, LET'S GO.

01:03:22.083 --> 01:03:23.041
COPY THAT.

01:03:23.041 --> 01:03:23.959
WHO THE FUCK IS SHE?

01:03:23.959 --> 01:03:26.125
WE JUST I.D.ed HER.
LIBERTY WALLACE.

01:03:26.125 --> 01:03:28.500
THE VP OF McCLOUD.
MARRIED TO THE CEO.

01:03:28.500 --> 01:03:30.875
CONNECTIONS
UP THE WAZOO.

01:03:30.875 --> 01:03:32.083
JESUS CHRIST.
I KNOW HIM. VICTOR.

01:03:32.083 --> 01:03:34.834
YEAH, WE'RE TRYING
TO TRACK HIM DOWN
RIGHT NOW.

01:03:34.834 --> 01:03:36.709
THEN THERE'S NO WAY
SHE'S WITH THE SHOOTER.

01:03:36.709 --> 01:03:37.125
SHE'S A HOSTAGE.

01:03:38.291 --> 01:03:41.834
SO I'M BAIT?

01:03:41.834 --> 01:03:44.458
NO. MORE LIKE...

01:03:44.458 --> 01:03:48.542
MORE LIKE A SHOWPIECE.

01:03:48.542 --> 01:03:52.709
I LIKE YOUR
RECKLESS SIDE.

01:03:52.709 --> 01:03:55.625
YOU TRAVELED WITHOUT
YOUR BODYGUARD

01:03:55.625 --> 01:03:58.417
5 HOURS EVERY WEEK
AND SOMETIMES TWICE.

01:03:58.417 --> 01:04:00.667
YOU WERE A LITTLE BIT
MORE ACCESSIBLE

01:04:00.667 --> 01:04:02.667
AND PREDICTABLE THAN
THE PRESIDENT'S WIFE.

01:04:02.667 --> 01:04:05.500
SO WHO'S PISSED OFF
AT VICTOR?

01:04:05.500 --> 01:04:05.959
THE PRESIDENT?

01:04:08.834 --> 01:04:10.125
[SIGHS]

01:04:14.458 --> 01:04:15.875
NO.

01:04:19.166 --> 01:04:22.083
IT'S ALL ME
THIS TIME.

01:04:24.333 --> 01:04:27.166
I WAS A DAD.

01:04:27.166 --> 01:04:30.709
I'M NOT ANYMORE.

01:04:32.959 --> 01:04:34.083
SOMEBODY'S PULLING
YOUR STRING. WHO IS IT?

01:04:36.834 --> 01:04:38.333
NO ONE.

01:04:38.333 --> 01:04:41.000
NOT NOW.

01:04:41.000 --> 01:04:46.208
NEVER THOUGHT MY SKILLS
FROM MY FORMER LIFE
WOULD EVER PAY OFF.

01:04:46.208 --> 01:04:47.208
CIA?

01:04:51.375 --> 01:04:53.834
[LAUGHS] WELL...

01:04:54.667 --> 01:04:57.542
THAT, TOO.

01:04:57.542 --> 01:04:58.625
WELL, COME ON,
IF I'M GOING TO DIE,

01:04:58.625 --> 01:05:01.875
I HAVE THE RIGHT TO KNOW
MY ASSASSIN A LITTLE BETTER.

01:05:03.542 --> 01:05:05.500
I WORKED COVERT.

01:05:05.500 --> 01:05:08.542
COVERT OPERATIONS
FOR THE CIA.

01:05:08.542 --> 01:05:10.417
I WAS IN CHINA DURING
TIANANMEN SQUARE.

01:05:10.417 --> 01:05:13.750
CUBA, PANAMA.

01:05:13.750 --> 01:05:15.834
AND I WAS
IN COLUMBIA...

01:05:15.834 --> 01:05:18.041
WHEN MY DAUGHTER
WAS KILLED.

01:05:41.709 --> 01:05:44.458
THIS IS CAPTAIN HANK WILFORD.

01:05:44.458 --> 01:05:47.166
CAN YOU TELL US
WHAT THIS IS ABOUT?

01:05:49.333 --> 01:05:50.917
I DON'T WANT
ANYONE ELSE TO DIE

01:05:50.917 --> 01:05:52.417
BECAUSE THEY'RE
TALKING TO ME, JOE.

01:05:52.417 --> 01:05:54.166
SO WHAT'S IT
GOING TO BE?

01:05:54.166 --> 01:05:55.083
MM-MM-MM.

01:05:55.083 --> 01:05:56.667
IT'S YOUR SHOW, BABY.

01:05:56.667 --> 01:05:59.583
JUST LEAVE ME
OUT OF THIS FOR NOW.

01:06:01.625 --> 01:06:05.625
Liberty: THERE'S A BOMB
IN THE HOT DOG CART!

01:06:05.625 --> 01:06:08.959
IT'S SET TO BLOW WHEN
MY CELL PHONE DIES!

01:06:08.959 --> 01:06:11.458
IN ABOUT 15 MINUTES.

01:06:11.458 --> 01:06:14.458
I'M CHAINED TO THE CART!

01:06:15.041 --> 01:06:17.959
WHAT ARE THE DEMANDS?

01:06:17.959 --> 01:06:22.792
A PUBLIC DEBATE
OF THE SECOND AMENDMENT!

01:06:22.792 --> 01:06:23.750
HMM.

01:06:23.750 --> 01:06:25.291
HEARD OF IT?

01:06:25.291 --> 01:06:26.709
GO, GIRL.
[LAUGHS]

01:06:26.709 --> 01:06:28.750
I'D LIKE TO UNDERSTAND.

01:06:28.750 --> 01:06:29.709
ARE THERE ANY OTHER DEMANDS?

01:06:29.709 --> 01:06:32.166
CAN I COME CLOSER?

01:06:32.166 --> 01:06:34.917
ANY OTHER DEMANDS?

01:06:34.917 --> 01:06:36.000
NO.

01:06:36.000 --> 01:06:37.083
NO!

01:06:46.000 --> 01:06:47.750
LIBERTY,

01:06:47.750 --> 01:06:50.667
I WILL KILL
ANYONE WHO COMES CLOSE.

01:06:50.667 --> 01:06:52.291
WE HAVE NO CONFIRMATION YET,
BUT IT APPEARS

01:06:52.291 --> 01:06:56.166
THAT KNBS REPORTER
BILL TOLLMAN HAS BEEN
SERIOUSLY HURT

01:06:56.166 --> 01:06:59.125
AND THAT LIBERTY WALLACE
OF McCLOUD GUNS

01:06:59.125 --> 01:07:00.834
IS DEMANDING
A PUBLIC DEBATE

01:07:00.834 --> 01:07:02.125
ABOUT THE CONSTITUTION

01:07:02.125 --> 01:07:05.041
AND ITS ROLE
IN OUR VIOLENT TIMES.

01:07:05.917 --> 01:07:06.500
SHE'S GRANDSTANDING.
GOTTA BE MILITIA.

01:07:06.500 --> 01:07:08.875
SIR.

01:07:08.875 --> 01:07:09.959
YEAH? YES, SIR.

01:07:09.959 --> 01:07:12.417
YES, SIR.
LIBERTY WALLACE.

01:07:12.417 --> 01:07:14.333
YOU WERE GOOD
UNDER THE PRESSURE,

01:07:14.333 --> 01:07:16.667
AND THE WHOLE WORLD
WILL APPLAUD YOU.

01:07:16.667 --> 01:07:18.667
OR LAUGH AT ME.

01:07:18.667 --> 01:07:20.917
THE PRESS IS
THE LEAST OF MY CONCERNS
AT THIS POINT.

01:07:20.917 --> 01:07:22.125
I'LL TRY TO MOVE
THEM BACK, BUT, UH...

01:07:24.709 --> 01:07:25.667
YES, SIR. I'LL MOVE
THEM BACK RIGHT AWAY.

01:07:25.667 --> 01:07:27.834
THANK YOU, SIR.

01:07:27.834 --> 01:07:29.542
GET RID OF THE PRESS.
TELL THEM IT'S A SAFETY ISSUE.

01:07:29.542 --> 01:07:31.375
UPTOWN DOESN'T WANT
THIS THING UNDER A MICROSCOPE.

01:07:31.375 --> 01:07:33.000
THEY'RE GOING
TO MAKE A MOVE, JOE.

01:07:33.000 --> 01:07:34.792
THEY'LL NEVER
DISARM THAT BOMB.

01:07:34.792 --> 01:07:37.166
THEY'VE PROBABLY
ALREADY GUESSED THAT.

01:07:37.166 --> 01:07:40.125
YOU WON'T BE ALONE
IN THE FINAL MOMENT.

01:07:42.166 --> 01:07:43.667
[SIGHS]

01:07:43.667 --> 01:07:44.709
Hank: STATUS ON THE THEATER?

01:07:44.709 --> 01:07:46.375
Mac: SOMEBODY WELDED
ALL THE SIDE EXITS SHUT.

01:07:46.375 --> 01:07:47.041
WE'VE GOT
AN ENTRY TEAM COMING IN,

01:07:47.041 --> 01:07:47.834
BUT THE FIRE DEPARTMENT--

01:07:47.834 --> 01:07:50.041
IS STUCK IN TRAFFIC.

01:07:50.041 --> 01:07:51.333
ALL EXITS?

01:07:51.333 --> 01:07:52.542
YEAH. OUR CUTTERS
WON'T WORK.

01:07:52.542 --> 01:07:53.583
THE ONLY EXIT
IS ON TO THE STREET

01:07:53.583 --> 01:07:56.041
THROUGH
THE FRONT DOOR.

01:07:56.041 --> 01:07:57.291
200 FUCKING HOSTAGES.

01:08:07.792 --> 01:08:09.333
TELL ME ABOUT
YOU DAUGHTER AGAIN.

01:08:11.333 --> 01:08:13.375
[SIGHS]

01:08:19.834 --> 01:08:22.207
A BOY AT SCHOOL
PUT A GUN TO HER HEAD

01:08:22.207 --> 01:08:26.834
AND ASKED HER
IF SHE BELIEVED IN GOD.

01:08:26.834 --> 01:08:27.750
WHAT DID SHE SAY?

01:08:27.750 --> 01:08:30.207
I DON'T KNOW.

01:08:30.207 --> 01:08:31.709
[ECHO]
What did she say?

01:08:31.709 --> 01:08:33.332
[ECHO]
I don't know.

01:08:41.750 --> 01:08:42.250
THAT ROBOT READY TO GO?

01:08:42.250 --> 01:08:43.125
Man:
BE HERE IN 15.

01:08:43.125 --> 01:08:45.207
Hank: WHAT ABOUT
THE BOMB TRUCK?

01:08:45.207 --> 01:08:46.834
WE GOT ONE
COMING IN FROM THE 48.

01:08:46.834 --> 01:08:47.750
ETA 30 MINUTES.

01:08:47.750 --> 01:08:49.709
GENERAL EVACUATION?

01:08:49.709 --> 01:08:50.959
WE GOT
A PHONE TREE GOING.

01:08:50.959 --> 01:08:52.417
WE'RE GOING TO FIND
THIS SON OF A BITCH.

01:08:52.417 --> 01:08:53.082
IT'S JUST GOING
TO TAKE A LITTLE TIME.

01:08:53.082 --> 01:08:55.625
TELL ME ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

01:09:02.250 --> 01:09:04.166
MY FATHER.

01:09:10.709 --> 01:09:13.082
HE WAS MY HERO.

01:09:16.457 --> 01:09:18.250
HE WAS.

01:09:25.166 --> 01:09:27.207
AFTER HE, UM...

01:09:27.207 --> 01:09:29.792
YOU KNOW...

01:09:33.917 --> 01:09:36.500
I HAD TO LEAVE SCHOOL
TO EARN A LIVING,

01:09:36.500 --> 01:09:39.417
AND ONE THING
LED TO THE NEXT.

01:09:39.417 --> 01:09:40.834
[SIGHS]

01:09:40.834 --> 01:09:42.000
I FOUND MYSELF WORKING
IN THE FAMILY BUSINESS...

01:09:42.000 --> 01:09:44.959
NO LONGER FAMILY OWNED.

01:09:44.959 --> 01:09:46.625
CAPTAIN,
I ONLY GOT 10 GUYS.

01:09:46.625 --> 01:09:48.332
WE SHOULD BE FINE ONCE
THE 53rd SQUAD SHOW UP.

01:09:48.332 --> 01:09:51.082
THAT SHOULD BE ANOTHER,
UH, 10 OR 12 MINUTES.

01:09:51.082 --> 01:09:52.875
WE'RE NOT
GOING TO MAKE IT.

01:09:52.875 --> 01:09:54.082
Liberty: IT'S ALL I KNEW.

01:09:54.082 --> 01:09:56.000
ALONG CAME VICTOR.
HE WAS BRILLIANT,

01:09:56.000 --> 01:09:57.375
BUT HE COULD SAVE
MY FATHERS'S COMPANY.

01:09:57.375 --> 01:09:59.417
OUR FIRST BIG DEAL
WAS WITH THE SAUDIS.

01:09:59.417 --> 01:10:01.959
THE IRAQIS WERE SHOOTING US
WITH OUR OWN GUNS.

01:10:01.959 --> 01:10:04.834
WHAT DO PEOPLE THINK
THE GOVERNMENT DOES
WITH ALL THOSE USED WEAPONS?

01:10:04.834 --> 01:10:07.917
MELT THEM DOWN,
MAKE LITTLE SCULPTURES
OUT OF THEM?

01:10:07.917 --> 01:10:09.083
AFTER WE TOOK
THE COMPANY INTERNATIONAL,

01:10:09.083 --> 01:10:09.834
SUDDENLY WE WERE
IN A DIFFERENT LEAGUE.

01:10:09.834 --> 01:10:13.250
IT GOT COMPLICATED.

01:10:13.250 --> 01:10:16.000
HERE I AM.

01:10:16.000 --> 01:10:19.208
AND RUSSELL MADE YOU
FEEL HUMAN AGAIN.

01:10:19.208 --> 01:10:22.542
AND ANONYMOUS.

01:10:22.542 --> 01:10:27.041
YOU KNOW, MY GREAT,
GREAT GRANDFATHER...

01:10:27.041 --> 01:10:29.041
HE DESIGNED THE GUN
THAT CHANGED THE OUTCOME

01:10:29.041 --> 01:10:33.375
OF THE CIVIL WAR.
[LAUGHS]

01:10:33.375 --> 01:10:35.834
I GREW UP THINKING
THAT'S WHAT WE WERE
STILL DOING.

01:10:35.834 --> 01:10:38.875
[PANICKED SHOUTING]

01:10:38.875 --> 01:10:40.875
Policeman, on bullhorn:
WE HAVE TO CLEAR
THE BUILDING.

01:10:40.875 --> 01:10:42.917
STAND BACK...

01:10:42.917 --> 01:10:45.834
LET ME OUT OF HERE,
PLEASE!

01:10:45.834 --> 01:10:48.166
QUIET.
QUIET, PLEASE!

01:10:52.250 --> 01:10:55.917
I'M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT YOUR DAUGHTER.

01:11:14.875 --> 01:11:16.458
Liberty: JOE?

01:11:35.583 --> 01:11:40.458
ONE LEFT BREATHING
TO HELP US TELL
OUR STORY.

01:11:40.458 --> 01:11:41.917
Pilot: WE'VE GOT THE SHOOTER
ON THE ROOF OF THE BUILDING

01:11:41.917 --> 01:11:44.333
AT EIGHTH AND GRACE.

01:11:46.417 --> 01:11:48.417
I DON'T CARE
IF IT LOOKS LIKE

01:11:48.417 --> 01:11:50.625
THE RUSSIANS
OR THE PAKISTANIS
OR THE GIRL SCOUTS.

01:11:50.625 --> 01:11:52.166
THE GUY'S VOICE
IS AMERICAN.

01:11:52.166 --> 01:11:54.834
THIS IS
AN INTERNAL THING.
GET ON IT.

01:11:54.834 --> 01:11:55.458
I WANT TO KNOW
WHO THE FUCK ELSE

01:11:55.458 --> 01:11:57.792
IS SHOOTING AT MY WIFE!

01:11:57.792 --> 01:11:59.834
[BEEP BEEP]

01:11:59.834 --> 01:12:02.041
YEAH?

01:12:02.041 --> 01:12:05.959
Joe:
WHERE YOU GOIN'?

01:12:05.959 --> 01:12:07.166
WHY?

01:12:07.166 --> 01:12:10.125
[CHUCKLES]

01:12:10.125 --> 01:12:13.125
THE BEREAVED HUSBAND.

01:12:13.125 --> 01:12:15.333
Victor:
WHEN ARE YOU GONNA
STOP SCREWING AROUND

01:12:15.333 --> 01:12:17.083
AND TELL ME WHAT THIS
IS ALL ABOUT?

01:12:17.083 --> 01:12:19.500
[CHUCKLES]
AH...

01:12:19.500 --> 01:12:21.166
YOU'RE DOING IT
BY THE BOOK.

01:12:21.166 --> 01:12:23.125
GO ON A BUSINESS TRIP,

01:12:23.125 --> 01:12:26.041
BE UNAVAILABLE FOR COMMENT.

01:12:26.041 --> 01:12:28.000
TOUCH DOWN IN WASHINGTON
FOR A LITTLE FACE TIME

01:12:28.000 --> 01:12:30.083
WITH A CLIENT.

01:12:30.083 --> 01:12:31.834
CHECK THE TEMPERATURE.

01:12:31.834 --> 01:12:35.834
I DON'T REALLY HAVE
A WHOLE LOT OF CHOICE
IN THAT, NOW DO I?

01:12:35.834 --> 01:12:37.500
JOE?

01:12:40.500 --> 01:12:41.792
WE KNOW EACH OTHER,
DON'T WE?

01:12:41.792 --> 01:12:45.875
DON'T WE?

01:12:45.875 --> 01:12:48.917
YOU DO ANY TIME
IN SOUTH AMERICA?

01:12:48.917 --> 01:12:51.583
WELL, WHO DIDN'T?

01:12:51.583 --> 01:12:53.375
NONE OF US REALLY
CAME THROUGH THAT

01:12:53.375 --> 01:12:55.375
WITH OUR MENTAL HEALTH
INTACT, DID WE?

01:12:55.375 --> 01:12:57.166
I MEAN, GOD KNOWS
IT TOOK ME A WHILE

01:12:57.166 --> 01:12:58.000
TO PULL MY SHIT TOGETHER
WHEN I GOT BACK.

01:12:58.000 --> 01:13:01.542
YEAH. YEAH.

01:13:01.542 --> 01:13:03.709
IT'S A MENTAL HEALTH
THING.

01:13:05.709 --> 01:13:07.959
YOU TALK LIKE
A COMPANY MAN.

01:13:07.959 --> 01:13:10.709
OR, AT LEAST--
WELL, YOU WERE
A COMPANY MAN,

01:13:10.709 --> 01:13:11.750
BECAUSE GOD KNOWS
THEY'D NEVER GO

01:13:11.750 --> 01:13:13.291
FOR THIS KIND
OF THEATRICAL BULLSHIT.

01:13:13.291 --> 01:13:17.166
WHAT IS YOUR BEEF
WITH ME?

01:13:17.166 --> 01:13:19.959
THAT YOU'D RUN AWAY
AND LET THEM TAKE LIBERTY.

01:13:19.959 --> 01:13:22.917
THAT YOU'RE NOT MAN ENOUGH
TO STAND UP FOR YOUR WIFE.

01:13:22.917 --> 01:13:25.667
I HOPE YOU'RE IMPRESSED
WITH YOUR LIFE.

01:13:31.583 --> 01:13:32.959
GRACE AND NINTH.

01:13:32.959 --> 01:13:33.959
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT,
SIR?

01:13:33.959 --> 01:13:35.709
GRACE AND NINTH!

01:13:35.709 --> 01:13:36.834
YOU GOT IT.

01:13:47.750 --> 01:13:49.291
Swat member, over radio:
THE SHOOTER'S STILL OUT HERE.

01:13:49.291 --> 01:13:51.375
Mac: SHIT. WELL,
TAKE COVER FAST.

01:13:51.375 --> 01:13:53.750
THE SNIPER'S SHOOTING
AT OUR GUYS ON THE GROUND.

01:13:53.750 --> 01:13:55.583
HOW MANY DOWN?

01:13:55.583 --> 01:13:57.375
NO REPORT YET.

01:14:01.917 --> 01:14:03.083
Swat member: LUKE TO MAC.
WE HAVE A SHOOTER.

01:14:03.083 --> 01:14:04.041
WE GOT THE GUY
ON THE ROOF.

01:14:04.041 --> 01:14:06.000
NOBODY MOVES
TILL WE GET MORE
INFORMATION.

01:14:06.000 --> 01:14:06.667
UNDERSTOOD?

01:14:06.667 --> 01:14:08.625
HAIL, MARY,
FULL OF GRACE,

01:14:08.625 --> 01:14:09.375
THE LORD
IS WITH THEE.

01:14:09.375 --> 01:14:11.583
BLESSED ART THOU
AMONGST WOMEN.

01:14:11.583 --> 01:14:16.667
BLESSED IS THE FRUIT
OF THY WOMB, JESUS.

01:14:16.667 --> 01:14:18.792
Swat member:
LOOKS LIKE WE GOT
A PROBLEM UP HERE.

01:14:18.792 --> 01:14:20.291
THE GUY ON THE ROOF'S
NOT THE SNIPER.

01:14:20.291 --> 01:14:21.583
WELL, WHO THE FUCK
IS HE THEN?

01:14:21.583 --> 01:14:22.041
WHY IS HE SHOOTING
AT HER?

01:14:22.041 --> 01:14:24.250
NO REPORT YET.

01:14:24.250 --> 01:14:25.208
...PRAY FOR US SINNERS

01:14:25.208 --> 01:14:30.208
NOW AND AT THE HOUR
OF OUR DEATH, AMEN.

01:14:30.208 --> 01:14:32.834
CHUCK SAYS HE'S TALKING
GOLD STAR CLEARANCE.

01:14:32.834 --> 01:14:34.542
CIA?

01:14:34.542 --> 01:14:36.750
JESUS, GET HIM DOWN HERE
IF HE'S STILL BREATHING.

01:14:42.291 --> 01:14:44.750
JOE...

01:14:44.750 --> 01:14:47.542
WHAT IS ENOUGH?

01:14:47.542 --> 01:14:50.375
Joe: ARE YOU
BEGGING FOR LIVES?

01:14:52.959 --> 01:14:55.375
YES.

01:15:00.083 --> 01:15:01.792
WHERE ARE THE SHOTS
COMING FROM?

01:15:01.792 --> 01:15:03.959
MY GUYS ARE THINKING
THE BRICK,
MAYBE THE CONCRETE.

01:15:03.959 --> 01:15:06.250
I'M THINKING HIGHER
THAN THE SEVENTH
OR EIGHTH--

01:15:06.250 --> 01:15:07.291
WAY TOO MUCH
INFORMATION.

01:15:07.291 --> 01:15:07.792
STATUS ON BACKUP?

01:15:18.000 --> 01:15:21.458
[BEEPING]

01:15:21.458 --> 01:15:23.125
[SOFT EXPLOSION SOUND]

01:15:23.125 --> 01:15:25.291
[BEEPING RAPIDLY]

01:15:25.291 --> 01:15:27.625
May: IT WAS PROBABLY A HOAX.

01:15:27.625 --> 01:15:30.500
I THINK IT HAS
SOMETHING TO DO
WITH THE HUSBAND.

01:15:30.500 --> 01:15:32.500
RUSSELL'S BEEN
PLAYING WITH FIRE.

01:15:32.500 --> 01:15:34.542
WELL, NOW, DON'T
BE JEALOUS, DEAR.

01:15:34.542 --> 01:15:36.834
