01:15:36.834 --> 01:15:40.041
VICTOR KNEW YOUR VOICE.

01:15:42.750 --> 01:15:44.000
IS THIS SOME KIND OF SETUP?

01:15:44.000 --> 01:15:47.041
COME ON. NOW, THINK HARD
AND YOU'LL GET IT ALL
FIGURED OUT.

01:15:47.041 --> 01:15:48.917
WHAT THE FUCK
DO YOU MEAN, "THINK"?!

01:15:48.917 --> 01:15:50.208
COME ON, COME CLEAN.

01:15:50.208 --> 01:15:53.125
YOU'VE TAKEN MY LIFE.
YOU OWE ME THAT MUCH.

01:15:53.125 --> 01:15:55.709
