WANTS A LOT
OF VISIBILITY.

01:16:01.208 --> 01:16:02.709
OK, OK.
IT'S A STUPID THOUGHT.

01:16:02.709 --> 01:16:03.959
LOOK, YOU CAN'T
WRITE THIS OFF

01:16:03.959 --> 01:16:05.625
TO BE SOME
BIG CONSPIRACY.

01:16:05.625 --> 01:16:07.542
THAT'S WHAT'LL
CONFUSE THE FUCK
OUT OF ALL OF THEM.

01:16:07.542 --> 01:16:09.375
THINK. THINK ABOUT
HOW YOU'RE DOIN'
ON THE SCOREBOARD.

01:16:09.375 --> 01:16:12.417
