I WOKE UP ONE DAY

01:16:12.417 --> 01:16:14.041
AND SAID, "WOW,
IT'S GREAT TO BE

01:16:14.041 --> 01:16:15.875
IN THE LETHAL WEAPONS
BUSINESS."

01:16:15.875 --> 01:16:18.959
IT'S LIKE THE GUY
ON THE CORNER
WHO SELLS NEWSPAPERS.

01:16:18.959 --> 01:16:20.333
IT'S WHAT I DO.

01:16:20.333 --> 01:16:22.125
WHAT ELSE AM I GONNA DO?

01:16:22.125 --> 01:16:24.709
BE THE BOSS.
IT'S YOUR LIFE,
ISN'T IT?

01:16:24.709 --> 01:16:27.417
IF THE IDEA WAS FOR ME
TO SEE GOD,

01:16:27.417 --> 01:16:28.667
YOU'VE ACHIEVED IT.

01:16:28.667 --> 01:16:30.959
I MEAN, I PRAYED,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

01:16:30.959 --> 01:16:32.291
Mac: OK,
THE PARKING GARAGE.

01:16:32.291 --> 01:16:34.959
LET'S ASSEMBLE
IN THERE. LET'S GO.

01:16:34.959 --> 01:16:36.250
[NERVOUS CHATTERING]

01:16:36.250 --> 01:16:36.667
Swat member:
JUST FOLLOW ME, MA'AM.

01:16:36.667 --> 01:16:38.917
Woman: QUICK.

01:16:38.917 --> 01:16:39.917
