TO CALL--

01:16:39.917 --> 01:16:41.417
Swat member:
NO, YOU CAN'T.

01:16:44.959 --> 01:16:48.333
WHEN MY DAUGHTER
WAS KILLED,
MY WIFE CAME APART.

01:16:49.917 --> 01:16:52.667
WE MET THE PARENTS
OF THE KID WHO DID IT.

01:16:54.417 --> 01:16:57.917
HIS FATHER CRIED,

01:16:57.917 --> 01:16:59.250
AND HE TOLD US THAT
HE HAD TAUGHT HIS SON

01:16:59.250 --> 01:17:02.834
HOW TO USE A GUN SAFELY.

01:17:06.417 --> 01:17:07.792
NEVER SAW IT COMING.

01:17:09.834 --> 01:17:14.000
I WANTED TO KILL
THAT KID...

01:17:14.000 --> 01:17:16.917
AND I WANTED TO KILL
THE FATHER.

01:17:19.208 --> 01:17:24.458
BUT HERE I AM INSTEAD.

01:17:27.250 --> 01:17:29.959
I LIKE YOU.

01:17:33.000 --> 01:17:35.125
THIS IS NO WAY TO DIE.

01:17:36.959 --> 01:17:39.625
FOR US, THERE'S
NO OTHER WAY OUT.

01:17:41.166 --> 01:17:44.125
I'VE THOUGHT ABOUT THIS
FOR A LONG TIME.

01:17:44.125 --> 01:17:46.792
BOMB SQUAD WANTS US
TO MOVE FURTHER BACK.

01:17:46.792 --> 01:17:48.875
CAPTAIN,
IT'S VICTOR WALLACE
ON THE LINE.

01:17:48.875 --> 01:17:49.959
NOBODY MOVE.

01:17:54.250 --> 01:17:56.166
VICTOR, THANK YOU.

01:17:56.166 --> 01:17:59.250
Victor: HANK?

01:17:59.250 --> 01:18:00.959
JESUS CHRIST.

01:18:00.959 --> 01:18:02.709
YOU KNOW WHAT THIS
IS ABOUT?

01:18:02.709 --> 01:18:04.250
I WAS HOPING
YOU'D TELL ME.

01:18:04.250 --> 01:18:05.959
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

01:18:05.959 --> 01:18:07.458
WE FOUND A GUY ON A ROOF
SHOOTING AT HER.

01:18:07.458 --> 01:18:08.583
HE LOOKS CIA.

01:18:08.583 --> 01:18:09.500
YOU GET HIM?

01:18:09.500 --> 01:18:11.166
NO, SOMEBODY ELSE
SHOT HIM.

01:18:11.166 --> 01:18:12.834
THE GUY WE GOT'S
NOT THE SNIPER,

01:18:12.834 --> 01:18:14.208
OR MAYBE HE'S--
HE'S ONE OF 'EM.

01:18:14.208 --> 01:18:15.792
MY ASS IS HANGING OUT
HERE, VICTOR.

01:18:15.792 --> 01:18:16.959
I NEED YOU TO TELL ME
WHAT'S GOIN' ON.

01:18:16.959 --> 01:18:20.291
WHAT'S GOIN' ON?
WE'RE DEALIN'
WITH A NUTCASE.

01:18:20.291 --> 01:18:21.208
THAT'S WHAT'S GOIN' ON.

01:18:21.208 --> 01:18:22.750
YEAH, OR A TERRORIST
BUYING TIME.

01:18:22.750 --> 01:18:23.709
IT'S ONLY BEEN
1/2 AN HOUR,

01:18:23.709 --> 01:18:24.375
AND THE PRESS
IS STILL STACKING UP.

01:18:24.375 --> 01:18:27.000
I'M 5 MINUTES AWAY.

