01:18:35.458 --> 01:18:37.667
ALLEGING THAT EFFORTS
BY GOVERNMENT

01:18:37.667 --> 01:18:39.291
TO IMPOSE
GUN SAFETY MEASURES

01:18:39.291 --> 01:18:40.625
AMOUNTS TO A CONSPIRACY

01:18:40.625 --> 01:18:43.041
THAT VIOLATES
CONSTITUTIONAL
GUARANTEES

01:18:43.041 --> 01:18:44.542
OF FREE TRADE.

01:18:44.542 --> 01:18:46.083
WALLACE'S COMPANY,
McCLOUD GUNS,

01:18:46.083 --> 01:18:47.834
IS AT THE CENTER
OF THIS CONTROVERSY,

01:18:47.834 --> 01:18:48.500
BY REFUSING
TO BECOME SIGNATORY

01:18:48.500 --> 01:18:50.917
TO ANY GOVERNMENT PROPOSAL

01:18:50.917 --> 01:18:52.417
THAT LEGISLATES
MORE CONTROLS.

01:18:52.417 --> 01:18:54.208
New anchor: THANKS
FOR THAT BREAKING NEWS.

01:18:54.208 --> 01:18:56.583
NOW ON THE INTERNATIONAL--
[CHANNEL CHANGES]

