31 CITIES AND COUNTRIES
HAVE BROUGHT CHARGES

01:18:58.375 --> 01:18:59.834
AGAINST MANUFACTURERS,

01:18:59.834 --> 01:19:01.208
CLAIMING THEY'RE NOT
DOING ENOUGH

01:19:01.208 --> 01:19:02.667
TO KEEP GUNS OUT OF
THE HANDS OF CHILDREN

01:19:02.667 --> 01:19:03.542
AND CRIMINALS.

01:19:03.542 --> 01:19:04.625
APPARENTLY,
WALLACE IS STAGING

01:19:04.625 --> 01:19:06.208
A HIGH-STAKES PROTEST

01:19:06.208 --> 01:19:07.083
AGAINST THE VERY INDUSTRY

01:19:07.083 --> 01:19:09.750
THAT MADE HER FAMILY
FAMOUS IN AMERICA.

01:19:09.750 --> 01:19:10.834
BACK TO YOU, DENNIS.

01:19:10.834 --> 01:19:13.834
WE'RE IN
THE FINAL STRETCH,
LIBERTY.

01:19:13.834 --> 01:19:18.291
SO...WHAT'S YOUR PLAN?

01:19:19.125 --> 01:19:21.041
[VOICE CRACKING]
I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

01:19:22.417 --> 01:19:25.458
I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

01:19:30.125 --> 01:19:34.250
