TO DIE BECAUSE OF ME, TOO.

01:19:34.250 --> 01:19:36.000
ME, NEITHER.

01:19:42.417 --> 01:19:45.166
YOU KNOW, THE NRA
IS JUST GONNA SPIN THIS

01:19:45.166 --> 01:19:46.417
AND SAY IT'S BECAUSE
OF PEOPLE LIKE YOU

01:19:46.417 --> 01:19:47.750
WE NEED TO BE ARMED.

01:19:47.750 --> 01:19:53.250
WELL, I WAS AN HONEST,
LAW-ABIDING CITIZEN.

01:19:53.250 --> 01:19:55.083
BY THAT DEFINITION,
I DESERVE TO BE ARMED.

01:19:55.083 --> 01:20:00.083
AND I WAS ACTING OUT
AGAINST THE OPPRESSION
OF OUR FREEDOM.

01:20:05.083 --> 01:20:09.750
THERE IT IS, HUH?

01:20:09.750 --> 01:20:12.208
[HORNS HONKING]
[HELICOPTER OVERHEAD]

01:20:19.291 --> 01:20:22.500
YOU KNOW, I FIRST
SAW YOU IN JERUSALEM

01:20:22.500 --> 01:20:24.291
ABOUT 3 YEARS AGO.

01:20:24.291 --> 01:20:26.959
YOU MUST HAVE MADE
A HELL OF A DEAL,

01:20:26.959 --> 01:20:30.375
'CAUSE THEY WERE
KISSING YOUR ASS.

01:20:33.792 --> 01:20:34.792
DID I MEET YOU?

01:20:34.792 --> 01:20:35.083
NO.

01:20:38.291 --> 01:20:40.417
I DID BUSINESS
WITH VICTOR, THOUGH,

01:20:40.417 --> 01:20:41.917
ON BEHALF OF THE SAUDIS.

01:20:41.917 --> 01:20:45.291
SEEMS HE LIKES TO SELL
ON ALL SIDES.

01:20:45.291 --> 01:20:48.834
WE MET
IN OUR EARLY DAYS.

01:20:48.834 --> 01:20:53.834
SERIOUSLY FLAWED MISSION
INTO COLOMBIA.

01:20:53.834 --> 01:20:55.583
I SAVED HIS LIFE.

01:20:55.583 --> 01:20:59.458
[CHUCKLES]
I'M FUNNY.

01:20:59.458 --> 01:21:03.166
I SAVED THE LIFE
OF THE MAN THAT
KILLED MY DAUGHTER.

01:21:13.000 --> 01:21:15.000
JOE?

01:21:16.625 --> 01:21:19.750
Daughter's voice:
DADDY?

01:21:27.208 --> 01:21:29.417
[HORN HONKS]

01:21:29.417 --> 01:21:32.041
[CAR ALARM WAILING]

01:21:38.375 --> 01:21:41.291
VICTOR, I DON'T FEEL
GOOD ABOUT THIS.

01:21:55.208 --> 01:21:59.291
DEATH ISN'T AS EXCITING
AS I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE.

01:22:02.583 --> 01:22:04.917
[CROWD COMMOTION]

01:22:10.166 --> 01:22:12.083
Victor: EXCUSE ME, PLEASE.

01:22:12.083 --> 01:22:14.750
EXCUSE ME.

01:22:14.750 --> 01:22:16.291
EXCUSE ME,
I'M VICTOR WALLACE.

01:22:16.291 --> 01:22:17.750
HEY, SIR, YOU CAN'T
COME THROUGH HERE.

01:22:17.750 --> 01:22:20.250
I'M THE HUSBAND,
YOU FUCKING MORON.

01:22:20.250 --> 01:22:22.250
Reporter: SIR,
JUST ONE QUESTION.

01:22:22.250 --> 01:22:23.583
SORRY, I CAN'T
TALK TO YOU.

01:22:23.583 --> 01:22:24.834
I CAN'T TALK TO YOU NOW.

01:22:24.834 --> 01:22:26.333
IS THIS RELATED
TO McCLOUD'S POSITION

01:22:26.333 --> 01:22:28.417
ON GUN SAFETY
LEGISLATION?

01:22:36.041 --> 01:22:38.083
THIS HAS ABSOLUTELY
NOTHING TO DO

01:22:38.083 --> 01:22:39.917
WITH McCLOUD INDUSTRIES.

01:22:39.917 --> 01:22:43.375
THESE ARE THE ACTIONS
OF AN INSANE MAN,

01:22:43.375 --> 01:22:45.917
AND MY WIFE
IS A WONDERFUL WOMAN.

01:22:47.417 --> 01:22:49.709
SHE'S A WONDERFUL WOMAN.

01:22:51.000 --> 01:22:53.417
Reporter: DID YOU HEAR THAT?
DID YOU GET THAT?

01:22:54.792 --> 01:22:56.083
VICTOR, YOU CAN'T GO
OUT THERE.

01:22:56.083 --> 01:22:57.166
I JUST WANT
TO LET HER SEE ME.

01:22:57.166 --> 01:22:58.208
WHY?

01:22:59.333 --> 01:23:02.458
[WHISPERING]
'Cause I think I know
who this guy is,

01:23:02.458 --> 01:23:04.208
and I think I can
get her out of this.

01:23:04.208 --> 01:23:06.625
WHATEVER YOU'RE THINKING,
I CAN'T--

01:23:06.625 --> 01:23:08.792
THIS IS MY PROBLEM.

01:23:08.792 --> 01:23:13.041
DON'T MAKE ME
MAKE PROBLEMS FOR YOU.

01:23:13.041 --> 01:23:14.250
YOU'RE GOOD TO THE CAR.

01:23:14.250 --> 01:23:17.500
Reporter: LOOK,
THERE'S NO DOUBT--
HE'S GOING OUT THERE.

01:23:17.500 --> 01:23:19.208
I SAID THE CAR!

01:23:23.625 --> 01:23:24.291
Victor: LIBERTY!

01:23:24.291 --> 01:23:26.625
Liberty, quietly:
VICTOR.

01:23:29.625 --> 01:23:32.333
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

01:23:35.750 --> 01:23:38.125
HEY, ALEX.

01:23:38.125 --> 01:23:42.458
WELL...
HERE WE ARE AGAIN...

01:23:42.458 --> 01:23:44.542
IN THE KILL ZONE.
WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU?

01:23:44.542 --> 01:23:47.333
I REMEMBER THE DAY
YOU WEPT LIKE A BABY

01:23:47.333 --> 01:23:50.667
WHILE I PROMISED
NOT TO LET YOU DIE.

01:23:50.667 --> 01:23:53.083
OK, OK,
YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

01:23:53.083 --> 01:23:57.083
YEAH. WASN'T I THANKFUL
ENOUGH THEN?

01:23:57.083 --> 01:23:58.500
WELL, THANKS AGAIN.
I MEAN IT.

01:23:58.500 --> 01:24:03.834
BUT I HAVE A FEELING
THAT WHAT'S REALLY
ACTUALLY EXPECTED OF ME

01:24:03.834 --> 01:24:07.083
IS SOME SORT OF BIG
PUBLIC CONFESSION.

01:24:07.083 --> 01:24:09.208
AM I RIGHT? WHAT AM I
SUPPOSED TO SAY?

01:24:12.542 --> 01:24:13.542
JOE, DON'T DO IT.

01:24:13.542 --> 01:24:16.291
THAT THAT--THAT REALLY
SHINY ONE THAT I HAVE

01:24:16.291 --> 01:24:18.959
IS ACTUALLY FOR--FOR
LEADING A BUNCH OF MEN
TO THEIR DEATH?

01:24:18.959 --> 01:24:21.375
IS THAT WHAT
I'M SUPPOSED TO SAY?

01:24:21.375 --> 01:24:25.208
COME ON.
ALEX, IT'S A WAR.

01:24:25.208 --> 01:24:28.041
THAT'S THE KIND OF STUFF
THAT HAPPENS.

01:24:28.041 --> 01:24:29.834
YOU THINK
I'M PROUD OF IT?

01:24:29.834 --> 01:24:31.417
I DIDN'T ASK
FOR THE MEDAL.

01:24:36.667 --> 01:24:38.291
YOUR DEATH IS GONNA
MEAN SOMETHING.

01:24:39.834 --> 01:24:42.500
BUT MY DAUGHTER'S WON'T.

01:24:44.458 --> 01:24:45.583
JOE, DON'T DO IT.

01:24:46.709 --> 01:24:47.458
DON'T DO IT!

01:24:47.458 --> 01:24:50.583
CHRIST, HE'S BEEN HIT.
DON'T!

01:24:50.583 --> 01:24:52.083
GET 'EM OUT OF HERE!
GO! GO!

01:24:52.083 --> 01:24:55.208
MOVE! MOVE!

01:25:07.917 --> 01:25:10.583
GET HIM INSIDE, FAST.

01:25:10.583 --> 01:25:11.125
COME ON, COME ON. MOVE!

01:25:11.125 --> 01:25:14.625
LET'S GO. LET'S GO.

01:25:18.875 --> 01:25:20.000
[EXPLOSION]

