[PANICKED CRIES]

01:25:22.166 --> 01:25:23.542
Liberty: DON'T!

01:25:30.250 --> 01:25:33.208
Joe: LIBERTY.

01:25:33.208 --> 01:25:35.667
LIBERTY! IT'S TIME.
WHAT?!

01:25:35.667 --> 01:25:36.834
TIME FOR YOU TO GO.

01:25:36.834 --> 01:25:38.000
THE KEYS FOR YOUR CUFFS

01:25:38.000 --> 01:25:40.542
IS IN A BOX
STUCK TO THE UNDERSIDE

01:25:40.542 --> 01:25:41.792
OF THE CART
NEAR THE CORNER.

01:25:41.792 --> 01:25:43.458
OK, GUYS. IT'S GOTTA
BE THIS ONE RIGHT HERE.

01:25:43.458 --> 01:25:44.000
SEVENTH AND ALVARADO.
MOVE ON IT.

01:25:44.000 --> 01:25:45.208
SEVENTH AND ALVARADO.

01:25:45.208 --> 01:25:48.583
[HELICOPTER HOVERING]
[SIRENS WAILING]

01:25:54.959 --> 01:25:56.166
AAH!

01:25:56.166 --> 01:25:58.625
BRING THE CHOPPER
INTO THE BACK OF THE SKYPORT

01:25:58.625 --> 01:26:00.375
RIGHT OUT OF THE SKY.

01:26:00.375 --> 01:26:02.417
HE'S SOME KIND OF SHOOTER
IF HE'S HOLED UP
THAT FAR AWAY.

01:26:09.291 --> 01:26:11.291
IN THE THEATER.
OFFICER NEEDS BACKUP.

01:26:11.291 --> 01:26:13.250
THERE'S PEOPLE PANICKING,
SMOKE EVERYWHERE.

01:26:13.250 --> 01:26:15.625
A FIRE'S BEEN SET
OR SOMETHING.

01:26:28.709 --> 01:26:30.875
GET BACK! THERE'S A BOMB!

01:26:30.875 --> 01:26:33.166
THERE'S A BOMB!

01:26:33.166 --> 01:26:34.250
GUYS, ALL EYES OUT
FOR THE WALLACE WOMAN.

01:26:34.250 --> 01:26:37.542
GET BACK! NO!
THERE'S A BOMB!

01:26:42.959 --> 01:26:45.709
THERE'S A BOMB!

01:26:45.709 --> 01:26:46.667
OH!

01:26:46.667 --> 01:26:47.875
Joe: LIBERTY,

01:26:47.875 --> 01:26:50.041
IT'S UP TO YOU NOW.

01:26:50.041 --> 01:26:52.125
TIME TO CHOOSE.

01:26:56.750 --> 01:26:59.750
[SIREN]

01:27:23.500 --> 01:27:25.333
Computer voice:
VIDEO ATTACHMENT
IS STREAMING.

01:27:25.333 --> 01:27:30.208
SENATOR LIBBY TOOK
