IN CASH.

01:27:30.208 --> 01:27:33.333
SENATOR LIPTON KRICK,
CONGRESSMAN GOMEZ.

01:27:33.333 --> 01:27:36.583
CHECK GENEVA
BANK ACCOUNTS...

01:27:36.583 --> 01:27:38.875
YOU'LL ALL BE ABLE
TO RETURN TO YOUR CARS

01:27:38.875 --> 01:27:41.041
ONCE WE SECURE THE AREA.

01:27:41.041 --> 01:27:43.041
WHERE'S RUSSELL?
WHERE'S RUSSELL?

01:27:43.041 --> 01:27:45.500
I HAVEN'T SEEN HIM.
[COUGHING]

01:27:47.875 --> 01:27:50.917
RUSSELL! RUSSELL!

01:27:54.166 --> 01:27:56.458
RUSSELL!

01:27:56.458 --> 01:27:58.583
GET OUT OF HERE! GO!

01:28:01.000 --> 01:28:03.417
LIBERTY,
GET OUT OF HERE!
THERE'S A BOMB!

01:28:03.417 --> 01:28:05.166
GET OUT--NO!

01:28:05.166 --> 01:28:08.417
THERE'S A BOMB!
GET OUT OF HERE!
GET OUT!

01:28:17.667 --> 01:28:19.375
[SIGHS]

01:28:30.291 --> 01:28:33.959
Computer voice:
FILE WITH VIDEO
ATTACHMENT SENT.

01:28:41.458 --> 01:28:43.959
AS YOU CAN SEE,
THE AREA'S BEEN CONTAINED.

01:28:43.959 --> 01:28:45.959
THE SITUATION'S
UNDER CONTROL.

01:28:45.959 --> 01:28:48.458
NOW, UH, IF YOU'LL
EXCUSE ME...

01:29:04.208 --> 01:29:05.625
EVERYBODY IN THE ALLEY--
NOW! GO!

01:29:05.625 --> 01:29:07.709
RIGHT.
GET THE FIREMEN ON IT.

01:29:09.000 --> 01:29:10.834
FIND THAT MOTHERFUCKER!

01:29:23.667 --> 01:29:27.959
NO, SIR. NO OTHER CIVILIAN
CASUALTIES FROM THE EXPLOSIONS.

01:29:27.959 --> 01:29:30.250
WE'VE HAD A FIRE
REPORTED IN THE BACK
OF THE THEATER, SIR.

01:29:30.250 --> 01:29:32.625
NO DAMAGE,
NO CASUALTIES.

01:29:32.625 --> 01:29:33.917
ALL NOISE AND SMOKE.

01:29:33.917 --> 01:29:35.041
HE MADE ME SHOOT IT...

01:29:35.041 --> 01:29:38.667
AT CLOSE RANGE.

01:29:38.667 --> 01:29:40.625
[ALARM RINGS]

01:29:50.875 --> 01:29:52.333
WHO ARE YOU?

01:29:52.333 --> 01:29:54.166
I WAS LOOKING
FOR MY WIFE'S PURSE--

01:29:54.166 --> 01:29:55.250
IT'S NOT SAFE IN HERE.
GET OUT OF HERE.
COME ON.

01:29:55.250 --> 01:29:58.291
LOCK IT UP, RAY.
SURE.

